(80, 46, 'en', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">8 Tips For Showcasing Soft Skills On Your CV</span></span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">When it comes to highlighting soft skills on your CV, it&#39;s essential to be strategic in your approach. Here are some tips to help you effectively showcase these valuable attributes:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Tailor Your CV:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Customize your CV for each job application, emphasizing soft skills that are particularly relevant to the specific role. This ensures that your document aligns with the employer&#39;s expectations.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Use Action Verbs:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> When describing your experiences and achievements, use action verbs that reflect your soft skills. For instance, instead of stating, &quot;Responsible for team projects,&quot; say, &quot;Led and collaborated on cross-functional team projects, showcasing strong teamwork and leadership.&quot;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Provide Concrete Examples:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Back up your soft skills with specific examples from your experiences. If you&#39;re highlighting communication skills, mention instances where effective communication led to successful outcomes.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Highlight Achievements:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Create a separate section on your CV to showcase achievements related to your soft skills. This could include awards, commendations, or recognition for exceptional teamwork, leadership, or problem-solving.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Quantify When Possible:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> If you can quantify the impact of your soft skills, do so. For example, mention how your leadership increased team productivity by a certain percentage or how your effective communication resulted in improved client satisfaction.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Seek Feedback:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> If you&#39;ve received positive feedback from colleagues, supervisors, or clients regarding your soft skills, consider incorporating these testimonials (with permission) in your CV or cover letter.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Differentiate Hard and Soft Skills:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Start by understanding the difference between hard skills (tangible, teachable abilities) and soft skills (interpersonal and behavioral traits). Reserve a separate section for each on your CV.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Incorporate Keywords:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Tailor your CV to the job description by including relevant soft skill keywords mentioned in the job posting. This can improve your chances of passing through applicant tracking systems (ATS).</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Why Including Soft Skills Can Boost Job Prospects</span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Here&#39;s how emphasizing soft skills on your CV can enhance your job prospects:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Increased Relevance:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Highlighting soft skills makes your CV more relevant to employers looking for candidates who can contribute not only with technical skills but also with effective communication, leadership, and teamwork.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Differentiation:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> In a competitive job market, showcasing your soft skills sets you apart from other candidates with similar qualifications.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Versatility:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Soft skills are transferable across industries and roles, making you a versatile candidate capable of adapting to different work environments.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Positive Impression:</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"> Employers often value soft skills as indicators of your ability to integrate seamlessly into their organization&#39;s culture and contribute to a harmonious work environment.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">The Way To The Top: Invest In Your Soft Skills </span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Invest in developing your soft skills because they are the fuel that drives your professional journey. With the above soft skills, you will be ready to face the challenges of the working world confidently and effectively. Use these valuable skills not only to advance your career, but also to achieve your personal goals. Your success is in your hands &ndash; be bold, be determined and become the best version of yourself!</span></span></span></p>', NULL),
(81, 46, 'de', '<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">So pr&auml;sentierst Du Soft Skills in Deinem Lebenslauf</span></span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Wenn es darum geht, Soft Skills in Deinem Lebenslauf hervorzuheben, ist es wichtig, strategisch vorzugehen. Hier sind einige Tipps, um diese wertvollen Qualit&auml;ten wirkungsvoll zu pr&auml;sentieren:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Passe Deinen Lebenslauf an</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Stimme Deinen Lebenslauf auf jede Bewerbung ab und betone die Soft Skills, die f&uuml;r die jeweilige Stelle besonders wichtig sind. Dadurch gew&auml;hrleistest Du, dass Dein Dokument den Erwartungen des Arbeitgebers entspricht.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:48px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Verwende Aktionsverben</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Nutze bei der Beschreibung Deiner Erfahrungen und Leistungen handlungsbezogene Verben, die Deine Soft Skills widerspiegeln. Schreibe z. B. statt &bdquo;Verantwortlich f&uuml;r Teamprojekte&quot;: &bdquo;Ich habe funktions&uuml;bergreifende Teamprojekte <em>geleitet</em> bzw. daran <em>mitgewirkt </em>und dabei gute Teamarbeit und F&uuml;hrungsqualit&auml;ten bewiesen.&quot;</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Gib konkrete Beispiele</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Untermauere Deine Soft Skills mit konkreten Beispielen aus Deinen Erfahrungen. Wenn Du Kommunikationsf&auml;higkeiten hervorhebst, nenne Beispiele, in denen effektive Kommunikation zu erfolgreichen Ergebnissen gef&uuml;hrt hat.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Erfolge hervorheben</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Lege einen separaten Abschnitt in Deinem Lebenslauf an, in dem Du Deine Leistungen im Zusammenhang mit Deinen Soft Skills hervorhebst. Dazu k&ouml;nnten Auszeichnungen, Belobigungen oder Anerkennungen f&uuml;r au&szlig;ergew&ouml;hnliche Teamarbeit, F&uuml;hrungsqualit&auml;ten oder Probleml&ouml;sungen geh&ouml;ren.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"5\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Quantifiziere, wenn m&ouml;glich</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Wenn Du die Effekte Deiner Soft Skills quantifizieren kannst, dann tu das. Erw&auml;hne zum Beispiel, wie Deine F&uuml;hrungsqualit&auml;ten die Produktivit&auml;t des Teams um einen bestimmten Prozentsatz erh&ouml;ht haben oder wie Deine effektive Kommunikation zu einer h&ouml;heren Kundenzufriedenheit gef&uuml;hrt hat.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"6\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Hole Dir Feedback ein</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Wenn Du von Kollegen, Vorgesetzten oder Kunden positives Feedback zu Deinen Soft Skills erhalten hast, solltest Du diese Referenzen (mit Erlaubnis) in Deinen Lebenslauf oder Dein Anschreiben einbauen.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"7\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Unterscheide zwischen Hard Skills und Soft Skills</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Mache Dir zun&auml;chst den Unterschied zwischen Hard Skills (greifbare, lehrbare F&auml;higkeiten) und Soft Skills (zwischenmenschliche und verhaltensbezogene Eigenschaften) klar. Reserviere f&uuml;r beide einen eigenen Abschnitt in Deinem Lebenslauf.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"8\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Beziehe Keywords ein</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Passe Deinen Lebenslauf an die Stellenbeschreibung an, indem Du die in der Stellenausschreibung genannten Schl&uuml;sselw&ouml;rter zu den Soft Skills aufnimmst. Dadurch kannst Du Deine Chancen verbessern, von Bewerbermanagement-Systemen (Application Tracking System, ATS) erfasst zu werden.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Darum verbessern&nbsp;Soft Skills Deine Job-Chancen</span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Hier erf&auml;hrst Du, wie die Betonung von Soft Skills in Deinem Lebenslauf Deine Berufsaussichten verbessern kann:</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Erh&ouml;hte Relevanz</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Die Hervorhebung von Soft Skills erh&ouml;ht die Relevanz Deines Lebenslaufs f&uuml;r Arbeitgeber, die nach Bewerbern suchen, die nicht nur mit Fachkompetenz, sondern auch mit effektiver Kommunikation, F&uuml;hrungsqualit&auml;ten und Teamwork einen Beitrag leisten k&ouml;nnen.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:24px; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"2\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Differenzierung</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Auf einem umk&auml;mpften Arbeitsmarkt hebst Du Dich durch die Pr&auml;sentation Deiner Soft Skills von anderen Bewerbern mit &auml;hnlichen Qualifikationen ab.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"3\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Vielseitigkeit</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Soft Skills sind branchen- und funktions&uuml;bergreifend anwendbar und machen Dich zu einem flexiblen Bewerber, der sich an unterschiedliche Arbeitsumgebungen anpassen kann.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol start=\"4\">\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Positiver Eindruck</span></strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">: Arbeitgeber sch&auml;tzen Soft Skills oft als Indikator f&uuml;r Deine F&auml;higkeit, Dich nahtlos in die Unternehmenskultur zu integrieren und zu einem harmonischen Arbeitsumfeld beizutragen.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"contents\">\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Der Weg nach oben: Investiere in Deine Soft Skills </span></span></strong></span></span></h2>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\">Investiere in die Entwicklung Deiner Soft Skills, denn sie sind der Treibstoff, der Deine berufliche Reise antreibt. Mit den genannten f&uuml;nf Soft Skills bist Du bereit, den Herausforderungen der Arbeitswelt selbstbewusst und effektiv zu begegnen. Nutze diese wertvollen F&auml;higkeiten, um nicht nur Deine Karriere voranzutreiben, sondern auch Deine pers&ouml;nlichen Ziele zu erreichen. Dein Erfolg liegt in Deinen H&auml;nden &ndash; sei mutig, sei entschlossen und werde die beste Version Deiner selbst</span>.</span></span></p>', NULL),
