(3, 'Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA)', 'Bachelor of Business Administration Fast Track (BBA)', '<p>You already have professional experience? You&rsquo;re in luck. <strong>Shorten</strong> the duration of your <strong>studies</strong> to up <strong>to</strong>&nbsp;<strong>6&nbsp;months</strong>! With this variant of the BA Bachelor, you take your study in the fast lane. Study online as and when you want. Take a <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">degree shortcut</a> now!</p>', '/ff', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>BBA&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Benefits </strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-related education</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Up-to-date case studies</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Step-by-step support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Internationally recognized degree</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Facts At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor of Business Administration<strong> </strong>(BBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span>:</strong>&nbsp;1-2<strong>&nbsp;</strong>semesters</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span>: </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>: Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span>: </strong>180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:&nbsp;Completed vocational training<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/bachelor-degree#requirements\">&nbsp;(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Tuition Fee</strong></span>:&nbsp;11,900.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>: Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Get Qualified On The Fast Lane</strong></span></strong></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Full speed ahead to your Bachelor&#39;s degree! If you already have professional knowledge, you can save a lot of study time and tuition fees. Get your professional achievements <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">recognized</a> and become a BBA&nbsp;in only 6&nbsp;or 12 months. respectively. Because your time is precious.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Is The Fast-Track Variant Suitable For You?</strong></span></strong></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>It is the right choice if you want to obtain an internationally recognized degree in BA&nbsp;and have already completed relevant vocational training or gained relevant work experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Program Contain? </strong></span></strong></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Like the standard-track BBA, this bachelor degree too prepares you for a managerial career in industry and business. You will gain a broad overview of the basic BA subjects, including marketing, human resources, accounting and finance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In authentic Harvard case studies, you will acquire strategic and operational management know-how and learn how to analyze and assess business problems competently and generate effective solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>By the end of this program, you&#39;ll have the fundamental values and skills you need to be an added value to any organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Stay On The Right Track</strong></span></strong></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>The BBA program qualifies students to assume leadership roles in companies, organizations and public administration institutions. In addition, it opens up the possibility of taking up <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online/business-administration-course\">CAS</a> studies or <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/emba\">EMBA</a> studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><strong>&nbsp;</strong></strong></p>', 'bba-fast-track', 'BBA In 6 Months | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Accelerate your studies! With ONSITES Graduate School\'s Fast Track BBA. ✔ 6 or 12 months ✔ 100% online ✔ Internationally recognized degree. Apply now!', 4, 'en'),
(4, 'Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA)', 'Bachelor of Business Administration Fast-Track (BBA)', '<p>Du hast bereits berufliche Vorkenntnisse? Dann <strong>verk&uuml;rze</strong> Dein Bachelor-Studium <strong>auf</strong> bis zu <strong>6&nbsp;Monate</strong>! Mit dieser BBA-Variante studierst Du auf der &Uuml;berholspur. Online studieren wie und wann Du willst. Jetzt <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Studium verk&uuml;rzen</a>!</p>', '/fff', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Warum BBA mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Benefits</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Topaktuelle Fallstudien</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Schritt-f&uuml;r-Schritt Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Keine Pr&auml;senztermine</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">International anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Details im &Uuml;berblick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>1-2&nbsp;Semester</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>: Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassung</span></strong>:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>Abgeschlossene Berufsausbildung&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/bachelor#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;11.900,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>BWL studieren auf der Schnellspur</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mit Vollgas zum Bachelor-Abschluss! Wenn Du bereits fachliche Vorkenntnisse besitzt, kannst Du viel Studienzeit und Studiengeb&uuml;hren sparen. Lasse Dir Deine beruflichen Leistungen <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">anerkennen</a> und werde Bachelor in Bachelor Administration in nur <strong>6</strong>&nbsp;<strong>bzw.</strong> <strong>12 Monaten</strong>. Weil Deine Zeit kostbar ist.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Ist der Fast-Track BBA&nbsp;f&uuml;r Dich geeignet?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Fast-Track ist die richtige Wahl, wenn Du einen international anerkannten Bachelorabschluss in Betriebswirtschaft erlangen m&ouml;chtest und bereits eine entsprechende Berufsausbildung absolviert bzw. einschl&auml;gige Berufserfahrungen gesammelt hast.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Was sind die Studieninhalte?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wie das regul&auml;re Bachelor-Studium bereitet Dich auch die Schnellvariante des Bachelor of Business Administration&nbsp;auf eine Manager-Karriere in Industrie und Wirtschaft vor. Du erlangst einen breit angelegten &Uuml;berblick &uuml;ber die Grundlagenf&auml;cher der Betriebswirtschaftslehre, darunter Marketing, Human Resources, Rechnungswesen und Finance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In authentischen Fallstudien mit Harvard-Renommee erarbeitest Du Dir strategisch-operatives Management-Know-how und lernst, betriebswirtschaftliche Probleme kompetent zu analysieren, zu beurteilen sowie effektive L&ouml;sungen zu generieren.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Am Ende dieses Bachelor-Studiums besitzt Du die Grundwerte und Skills, die Du ben&ouml;tigst, um f&uuml;r jedes Unternehmen eine Bereicherung zu sein.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Auf der richtigen Spur bleiben</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Programm qualifiziert zur &Uuml;bernahme von F&uuml;hrungsaufgaben in Unternehmen, Organisationen und Institutionen der &ouml;ffentlichen Verwaltung. Zudem er&ouml;ffnet der Bachelor-Abschluss die M&ouml;glichkeit, ein <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online/bwl-kurs\">CAS-Online</a>-Studium oder <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/emba\">EMBA</a>-Studium aufzunehmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'bba', 'BBA in 6 Monaten | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Ausbildung abgeschlossen? Verkürze Dein BBA-Studium - auf 6 bzw. 12 Monate. Vorteile: ✔ Keine Präsenz ✔ Ohne Abitur ✔ Soforteinstieg. Jetzt mehr erfahren!', 4, 'de'),
(7, 'Master of Science in Digitalization', 'Master of Science in Digitalization', '<p>Do you want to take off in your career as a digital professional? Start a master&#39;s degree in digitalization. No attendance &amp; free time management. Get a master&#39;s degree while working. Become part of the digital transformation now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Reasons For A Master&rsquo;s With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-focused education</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Up-to-date study contents</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>High flexibility</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; comprehensive support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% location-independent</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Details At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Science (M.Sc.)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span>: </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>: Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/master-degree#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Booster: Master&#39;s Degree in Digitization</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top-fit for the digital future market! Digitization has become an omnipresent phenomenon in everyday and business life. Almost every industry is affected by the digital transformation and must adapt to the technology trend. This means that there is an enormous demand for specialists in the digital field.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Numerous business sectors are desperately seeking qualified specialists and managers to manage, coordinate and optimize digitized processes. With the Digitalization Master, you lay the solid foundation for a stellar career as a digital professional.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Is The Program Suitable For Me?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The program is just right for you if you want to advance professionally or change your career without having to interrupt your professional activity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Contents of the Digitalization Master</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a participant in the online program, you will be enabled through various modules to independently develop and implement digital solutions for companies in order to actively promote digital transformation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To this end, the degree combines practice-relevant know-how from both technology and management. In this way, you will acquire the necessary digital skills combined with essential digital technologies and modern management methods.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Towards the end of your studies, you will write a thesis to demonstrate your ability to work scientifically on an independent basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Digitization Jobs &ndash; Your Career Opportunities</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The program&nbsp;qualifies you for digitalization jobs such as digital business analyst, digital transformation officer, project manager or digital solution architect. Take the next step in your career now!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'digitalization', 'Master Of Science In Digitalization | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Join the digital transformation & become a digital specialist with our M.Sc. in Digitalization program. ✔ Online ✔ Personal support ✔ Low fees. Click here!', 6, 'en'),
(8, 'Master of Science in Digitalisierung', 'Master Digitalisierung (M.Sc.)', '<p>Du willst als Digital-Profi karrierem&auml;&szlig;ig durchstarten? Starte den Master Digitalisierung. Ohne Pr&auml;senzzeiten &amp; mit freier Zeiteinteilung. Master berufsbegleitend studieren. Jetzt Teil der digitalen Transformation werden!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r ein Master-Studium mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zeitgem&auml;&szlig;e Studieninhalte</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>100% ortsunabh&auml;ngig</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anerkannte Ausbildung</strong></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Daten im &Uuml;berblick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Master of Science (M.Sc.)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>: Bachelorabschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/master#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7.500,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Karriereturbo: Master Digitalisierung</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Topfit f&uuml;r den digitalen Zukunftsmarkt! Digitalisierung ist ein allgegenw&auml;rtiges Ph&auml;nomen im Alltags- und Gesch&auml;ftsleben geworden. Fast jede Branche ist vom digitalen Wandel betroffen und muss sich an den Technologietrend anpassen. Damit besteht ein enormer Bedarf an Spezialisten im digitalen Bereich.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zahlreiche Wirtschaftssektoren suchen h&auml;nderingend nach qualifizierten Fach- und F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;ften, um digitalisierte Prozesse zu steuern, zu koordinieren und zu optimieren. Mit dem Master Digitalisierung&nbsp;legst Du das feste Fundament f&uuml;r eine steile Karriere als Digitalprofi.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zielgruppe des Master Digitalisierung</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Studium&nbsp;ist genau das Richtige f&uuml;r Dich, wenn Du beruflich aufsteigen oder Dich beruflich ver&auml;ndern m&ouml;chtest, ohne Deine berufliche T&auml;tigkeit unterbrechen zu m&uuml;ssen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte des Master-Studiums</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Als Teilnehmer des Online-Studiums wirst Du durch verschiedene Module dazu bef&auml;higt, eigenst&auml;ndig digitale L&ouml;sungen f&uuml;r Unternehmen zu erarbeiten und durchzuf&uuml;hren, um so die digitale Transformation aktiv zu bef&ouml;rdern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zu diesem Zweck vereint der Master Digitalisierung praxisrelevantes Know-how aus Technologie und Management. Auf diese Weise erlangst Du die notwendigen Digitalskills verbunden mit zentralen Digitaltechnologien und modernen Managementmethoden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gegen Ende des Studiums verfasst Du eine Masterarbeit, um Deine F&auml;higkeit zum eigenst&auml;ndigen wissenschaftlichen Arbeiten unter Beweis zu stellen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Jobs Digitalisierung &ndash; Deine Berufschancen als Master</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Master Digitalisierung qualifizert Dich u.a. f&uuml;r T&auml;tigkeiten als Digital Business Analyst, Digital Transformation Officer, Projektmanager oder Digital Solution Architect. Gehe jetzt den n&auml;chsten Karriereschritt!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'digitalisierung-studium', 'Master Digitalisierung präsenzfrei | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Du suchst einen Job mit Zukunft? Bilde Dich digital weiter. Mit dem Master Digitalisierung. Online & berufsbegleitend. Auch ohne Erststudium. Jetzt informieren!', 6, 'de'),
(9, 'Master of Laws', 'Master of Laws (LL.M)', '<p>Want to start an international career as a business lawyer? Study for an LLM. Part-time &amp; fully online. Get 2 qualifications in 1: law &amp; business administration. <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/student-portal\">Apply</a> now and start any time!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Reasons For An&nbsp;LLM&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-oriented education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality learning&nbsp;materials</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Comprehensive personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Internationally recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Details</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Degree</strong></span>: Master of Laws (LL.M)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Language</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/master-degree#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>LLM: Education x 2</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Succeed at the interface between law and business. Whether you want to pursue a career in an international law firm or are drawn to the executive suite of international companies: this degree&nbsp;opens the door to you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The LLM Degree Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The online degree is not only suitable for LLB&nbsp;graduates who want to gain in-depth knowledge. In addition, the program&nbsp;offers the opportunity for a career-enhancing additional qualification for law graduates and graduates of a business law program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study Contents</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The program provides both comprehensive legal knowledge and sound business know-how, with the legal focus dominating.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In perfectly tailored, practice-relevant online modules, you will deal with business-relevant topics such as labor law and personnel management, insolvency law, insurance law, or white-collar criminal law, and acquire fundamental business knowledge in business administration, economics, management, and accounting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To prove your ability to work scientifically, you will write a master&#39;s thesis on a business law-related topic towards the end of your studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Job Opportunities</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a graduate of the program, you are qualified to support companies in designing and implementing their business processes in a legally sound manner. The combination of legal and economic expertise enables you to take on a wide range of tasks in business and administration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This includes working as a business consultant, mediator, insolvency administrator and in personnel and legal departments. As a business lawyer, you will be able to competently meet the complex requirements in various fields of law, analyze interdisciplinary cases and think strategically on your own.</p>', 'llm', 'LL.M.: Master Of Laws | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Develop legal expertise & strong business acumen. With our online Master of Laws (LL.M.) program. ✔ Flexible ✔ Harvard materials ✔ Personal support. Apply now!', 7, 'en'),
(10, 'Master of Laws', 'Master of Laws (LL.M)', '<p>Erh&ouml;he Deine Einstiegs- und Aufstiegschancen als Wirtschaftsjurist! Mit einem berufsbegleitenden Wirtschaftsrecht-Studium zum LLM.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Juristisch-betriebswirtschaftliche Doppelqualifikation sichern &amp; internationale Karriere starten. Jetzt <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/bewerbung-studium\">bewerben</a>, sofort einsteigen &amp; online Wirtschaftsrecht studieren!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r einen LLM mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisbezogene Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertige Lernmaterialien</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Umfassender pers&ouml;nlicher Support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Qualifikation</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Details kompakt</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Master of Laws (LL.M)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelorabschluss mit juristischer Qualifikation&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/master#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>&euro; 7.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Doppelt qualifiziert mit dem LLM</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Erfolgreich an der Schnittstelle zwischen Recht und Wirtschaft. Ganz gleich, ob Du eine Karriere in einer international agierenden Kanzlei anstrebst oder es Dich in die F&uuml;hrungsetage internationaler Unternehmen zieht: der LLM&nbsp;&ouml;ffnet Dir T&uuml;r und Tor.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich das Studium zum LLM?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Online-Studium eignet sich nicht nur f&uuml;r Bachelor of Laws-Absolventen, die vertiefte Kenntnisse erlangen m&ouml;chten. Zudem bietet dieser&nbsp;Master&nbsp;die M&ouml;glichkeit auf eine karrieref&ouml;rdernde Zusatzqualifikation f&uuml;r Jura-Absolventen und Absolventen eines Wirtschaftsrecht-Studiums.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte des Wirtschaftsrecht-Studiums</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Studium&nbsp;vermittelt sowohl umfassende juristische Kenntnisse als auch fundiertes betriebswirtschaftliches Know-how, wobei der juristische Schwerpunkt dominiert.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In perfekt zugeschnittenen, praxisrelevanten Online-Modulen setzt Du Dich mit betriebsrelevanten Themen wie Arbeitsrecht und Personalmanagement, Insolvenzrecht, Versicherungsrecht oder Wirtschaftsstrafrecht auseinander und erlangst grundlegendes Fachwissen in BWL, VWL, Management und Rechnungswesen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Um Deine F&auml;higkeit zum wissenschaftlichen Arbeiten nachzuweisen, verfasst Du gegen Ende des Wirtschaftsrecht-Studiums eine Master-Arbeit zu einem wirtschaftsrechtlichen Thema.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Berufschancen als LLM</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Als Absolvent dieses&nbsp;Wirtschaftsrecht-Studiums bist Du qualifiziert, um Unternehmen dabei zu unterst&uuml;tzen, ihre Gesch&auml;ftsprozesse rechtssicher zu gestalten und umzusetzen. Die Verzahnung von juristischer und &ouml;konomischer Fachkompetenz erm&ouml;glicht Dir die &Uuml;bernahme von vielf&auml;ltigen Aufgaben in Wirtschaft und Verwaltung.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hierzu geh&ouml;rt die T&auml;tigkeit als Unternehmensberater, Mediator, Insolvenzverwalter und die Arbeit in Personal- und Rechtsabteilungen. Als Wirtschaftsjurist bist Du in der Lage, den komplexen Anforderungen auf unterschiedlichen Rechtsgebieten kompetent zu begegnen, interdisziplin&auml;re F&auml;lle zu analysieren und eigenst&auml;ndig strategisch zu denken.</p>', 'llm', 'LL.M - Master of Laws | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Weg frei für die internationale Kanzlei! Der LLM macht\'s möglich. Wirtschaftsrecht studieren in 1 Jahr. Ortsunabhängig. Jetzt online Master of Laws werden!', 7, 'de'),
(11, 'Master of Public Health', 'Master of Public Health (MPH)', '<p>Career upgrade for health professionals. With a part-time public health master degree program. No attendance &amp; no waiting periods. Flexible design. Become a MPH online now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top 7 Reasons For An MPH&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES</em></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-oriented education</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Learning with<strong>&nbsp;</strong>prestige</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; comprehensive support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% location-independent</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Internationally recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Details At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Public Health (MPH)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/master-degree#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span>: </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Your Leap Into A Healthy Career</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Protect the health of society and make a career out of it - the MPH&nbsp;degree makes it possible. Especially in times of global crises such as epidemics and climate change, smart public health specialists are more in demand than ever. Seize this career opportunity!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is Eligible?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Whether you&#39;re already working as a professional or manager in a public health institution and want to expand your expertise, or you&#39;re a newcomer looking to gain valuable expertise in the field alongside your job, this degree is the right choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Degree Cover?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this interdisciplinary, application-oriented degree program, you will learn to identify causes of global diseases, explore the health status of society and analyze weaknesses in the health care system within the framework of several modules.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the practice-oriented teaching and high-quality Harvard case studies, you will be able to independently develop solutions for the present and the future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will demonstrate your scientific aptitude in the form of a final master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Job Opportunities As Master of Laws</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition to jobs in public and private healthcare institutions, this&nbsp;part-time degree program also qualifies you for public health jobs in health insurance companies, pharmaceutical companies or in corporate health management. Secure your career advantages now!</p>', 'mph', 'MPH - Master Of Public Health | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Upgrade your career with our online Master of Public Health (MPH) program. Enjoy ✔ Fair fees ✔ Personal support ✔ Internationally recognized degree. Apply now!', 8, 'en'),
(12, 'Master of Public Health', 'Master Public Health (MPH)', '<p>Karriere-Upgrade f&uuml;r Gesundheitsprofis. Mit einem berufsbegleitendem Public-Health-Studium. Ohne Pr&auml;senz &amp; ohne Wartezeiten. Flexible Gestaltung. Jetzt online Master Public Health werden!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Public Health studieren mit <em>ONSITES</em> - 7 Top-Gr&uuml;nde</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Lernen mit&nbsp;Prestige</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% ortsungebunden</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">International anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Detail&uuml;bersicht</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Public Health (MPH)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelorabschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/master#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7.500,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Public-Health-Studium: Dein Sprung in eine gesunde Karriere</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Gesundheit der Gesellschaft sch&uuml;tzen und dabei Karriere machen &ndash; der Master in Public Health macht&rsquo;s m&ouml;glich. Gerade in Zeiten globaler Krisen wie Epidemien und Klimawandel sind smarte Spezialisten f&uuml;r &Ouml;ffentliche Gesundheit gefragter denn je. Nutze diese Karrierechance!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Wer geh&ouml;rt zur&nbsp;Zielgruppe?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ganz gleich, ob Du bereits als Fach- oder F&uuml;hrungskraft in einer Institution des Gesundheitswesens arbeitest und Deine Kompetenz erweitern m&ouml;chtest oder Du Neueinsteiger bist, der sich neben dem Beruf wertvolles Know-how auf dem Gebiet der &ouml;ffentlichen Gesundheitsversorgung aneignen m&ouml;chte &ndash; dieses&nbsp;Master-Studium&nbsp;ist die richtige Wahl.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Welche Inhalte umfasst das Studium?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In diesem interdisziplin&auml;ren, anwendungsorientierten Studium lernst Du im Rahmen mehrerer Module Ursachen globaler Krankheiten zu erkennen, den Gesundheitszustand der Gesellschaft zu erkunden und Schw&auml;chen im Gesundheitssystem zu analysieren.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dank der praxisorientierten Lehre und hochwertiger Harvard-Fallstudien wirst Du dazu bef&auml;higt, eigenst&auml;ndig L&ouml;sungen f&uuml;r die Gegenwart und Zukunft zu entwickeln.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deine wissenschaftliche Eignung weist Du in Form einer abschlie&szlig;enden Master-Arbeit nach.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Perspektiven als Master Public Health</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Neben T&auml;tigkeiten in &ouml;ffentlichen und privaten Gesundheitseinrichtungen qualifiziert Dich das berufsbegleitende Online-Studium auch f&uuml;r Public-Health-Jobs in Krankenkassen, Pharmaunternehmen oder im betrieblichen Gesundheitsmanagement. Jetzt Karrierevorteile sichern!</p>', 'public-health-studium', 'Master Public Health in 1 Jahr | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Lust auf die besten Public-Health-Jobs? Der Master Public Health macht Dich zukunftsfit. 100% flexible Online-Weiterbildung. Auch ohne Bachelor. Jetzt klicken!', 8, 'de'),
(13, 'Executive Master of Business Administration (EMBA)', 'Executive MBA (EMBA)', '<p>Take the next step in your career! From executive to leadership excellence. With this distance learning program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Boost your leadership skills and increase your potential while working. Your advantage package for a career leap: Flexible, well-founded &amp; tailored to your needs. Start online now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Good Reasons For An EMBA With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-oriented education</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; extensive support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% digital</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited program</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Everything At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span>:</strong> Executive Master of Business Administration (EMBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span>:</strong> 12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span>: </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Language</span>: </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span>: </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span>: </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span>: </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span>: </strong>7,500.00&nbsp;&euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span>: </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Flexible MBA Program For Genuine Leaders</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Do you want to develop your leadership personality alongside your job, gain new perspectives and tap unused potential? Then the Executive MBA is the right program for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Target Group</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The EMBA is specifically tailored to working executives, junior managers and self-employed persons with several years of professional experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>This Is What The EMBA Covers</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The program imparts up-to-date management knowledge to prepare you consistently for the future challenges as a top manager.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You will acquire in-depth business know-how in all relevant management disciplines, precisely tailored to the requirements and needs of experienced managers. In addition, the practice-oriented character of the program enables you to immediately apply your newly acquired soft and hard skills in professional practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The degree is completed with a written master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Prospects</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a successful graduate of the program, you will be able to confidently develop and implement innovative and effective solutions to current challenges in the real business environment. You are fully endowed with in-depth leadership and management expertise as well as strong communication and collaboration skills.</p>', 'emba', 'EMBA: Executive MBA | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Take your career to the next level. Start an Executive MBA (EMBA) degree while working. ✔ Online ✔ High flexibility ✔ Accredited program. Learn more!', 9, 'en');
