(14, 'Executive Master of Business Administration (EMBA)', 'Executive MBA (EMBA)', '<p>Gehe den n&auml;chsten Karriereschritt! Von der F&uuml;hrungskraft zur F&uuml;hrungskoryph&auml;e. Mit dem EMBA-Fernstudium.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Berufsbegleitend Leadership Skills boosten &amp; Potential vergr&ouml;&szlig;ern. Dein Vorteilspaket f&uuml;r den Karrieresprung: Flexibel, fundiert &amp; bedarfsgerecht. Jetzt online starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 gute Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r einen EMBA mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Praxisnahe Lehre</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertige Inhalte</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% digital</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Akkreditiertes Studium</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alles auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>: Executive Master of Business Administration (EMBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>: 12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Sprache</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>: &euro; 7.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich <strong>(</strong><a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Flexibles MBA-Studium f&uuml;r echte F&uuml;hrungspers&ouml;nlichkeiten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du m&ouml;chtest neben dem Beruf Deine F&uuml;hrungspers&ouml;nlichkeit weiterentwickeln, neue Perspektiven erhalten und ungenutzte Potentiale aussch&ouml;pfen? Dann ist der Executive MBA das richtige MBA-Studium f&uuml;r Dich.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zielgruppe des EMBA</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Fernstudium zum Executive Master of Business Administration ist speziell zugeschnitten auf berufst&auml;tige F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte, Nachwuchsf&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte sowie Selbst&auml;ndige mit mehrj&auml;hriger Berufserfahrung.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Das beinhaltet die Weiterbildung</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Executive MBA vermittelt aktuelles Management-Wissen, um Dich konsequent f&uuml;r die k&uuml;nftigen Herausforderungen als Top-Manager zu wappnen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du erlangst fundiertes wirtschaftswissenschaftliches Know-how in allen einschl&auml;gigen Management-Disziplinen, passgenau aufbereitet gem&auml;&szlig; den Anforderungen und Bed&uuml;rfnissen erfahrener Manager. Zudem erm&ouml;glicht der praxisorientierte Charakter des EMBA-Studiums, dass Du Deine neu erlangten Soft- und Hard-Skills umgehend in der beruflichen Praxis einbringen kannst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Abgeschlossen wird der Executive-MBA mit einer schriftlichen Masterarbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Berufliche Perspektiven</span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Als erfolgreicher Absolvent des MBA-Programms bist Du in der Lage, innovative und effektive L&ouml;sungen f&uuml;r aktuelle Herausforderungen im realen Gesch&auml;ftsumfeld souver&auml;n zu entwickeln und umzusetzen. Du verf&uuml;gst &uuml;ber tiefgehendes F&uuml;hrungs- und Management-Fachwissen sowie ausgepr&auml;gte Kommunikations- und Kooperationskompetenz.</p>', 'emba', 'EMBA - Executive MBA | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Entfalte Dein Führungspotential! Mit dem EMBA startest Du voll durch! Top-Weiterbildung für Macher: ✔ Remote ✔ Praxisnah ✔ Ohne Erststudium. Jetzt informieren!', 9, 'de'),
(15, 'MBA in Leadership & Coaching', 'MBA Coaching & Leadership', '<p>2-in-1 advantage package for leadership luminaries! With the MBA Coaching &amp; Leadership, you get coaching education plus leadership training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Expand your leadership skills online and become a business coach. Flexible master&#39;s degree with practical relevance. Study part-time MBA online now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Why Study&nbsp;Coaching &amp; Leadership With <em>ONSITES</em>?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-related education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top&nbsp;learning quality</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Personal &amp; comprehensive support</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>No attendance</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Our MBA At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>: 60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Package Deal: Coaching Training + Leadership Training</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Pretty smart! With this&nbsp;MBA you benefit twice: You go through a coaching education&nbsp;while boosting your leadership skills. That pays off: Coaching is a market with enormous growth potential. Take advantage of it now!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Target Group</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;MBA is the right program for you if you have relevant professional experience and want to coach people with personnel responsibility as a business coach; or if you are a manager yourself and want to further develop your leadership personality through coaching training.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Content &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to be accepted and successfully establish yourself as a business coach, you need the right foundation! This is exactly what the two-part MBA program provides.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During the coaching training you receive the necessary tools to accompany entrepreneurs in an advisory capacity in achieving their entrepreneurial goals. The leadership part is about combining coaching and leadership methods in a targeted manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The master&#39;s thesis completes the program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Prospects</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;practice-based MBA program&nbsp;opens career opportunities both as a business coach and as a leader fit for the future.</p>', 'coaching-leadership', 'MBA In Coaching Leadership | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Become a business coach. With ONSITES Graduate School\'s online MBA in Leadership & Coaching. ✔ 2-in-1 package ✔ Low fees ✔ Recognized degree. Apply now!', 10, 'en'),
(16, 'MBA in Leadership & Coaching', 'MBA Leadership & Coaching-Studium', '<p>2-in-1 Vorteilspaket f&uuml;r F&uuml;hrungskoryph&auml;en! Mit dem MBA in Coaching Leadership: Coaching-Ausbildung plus Leadership-Studium.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Online Leadership Skills erweitern und Business Coach werden. Flexibles Master-Studium mit Praxisfokus. Jetzt berufsbegleitend studieren!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Warum ein Coaching-Studium mit <em>ONSITES</em>?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Praxisnahe Lehre</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top Lernqualit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% pr&auml;senzfrei</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Der MBA auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>: Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>: 60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelorabschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7.500,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Kombi-Paket: Coaching-Ausbildung + Leadership-Training</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ganz sch&ouml;n gerissen! Mit dem MBA in Leadership &amp; Coaching&nbsp;profitierst Du gleich zweimal: Du durchl&auml;ufst eine Coaching-Ausbildung und boostest zugleich Deine Leadership Skills. Das lohnt sich: Coaching ist ein Markt mit enormem Wachstumspotenzial. Jetzt aussch&ouml;pfen!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Ist das&nbsp;MBA Leadership &amp; Coaching-Studium das richtige f&uuml;r Dich?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Programm&nbsp;ist das richtige Studium f&uuml;r Dich, wenn Du einschl&auml;gige Berufserfahrung mitbringst und als Business-Coach Personen mit Personalverantwortung coachen willst; oder selber eine F&uuml;hrungskraft bist und Deine F&uuml;hrungspers&ouml;nlichkeit durch ein&nbsp;Coaching-Studium&nbsp;weiterentwickeln m&ouml;chtest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wer ernstgenommen werden und sich erfolgreich als Business Coach etablieren m&ouml;chte, ben&ouml;tigt den richtigen Unterbau! Genau das leistet dieses&nbsp;zweigliedrige Weiterbildungsstudium.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>W&auml;hrend der Coaching-Ausbildung erh&auml;ltst Du das n&ouml;tige Handwerkszeug, um Unternehmer bei der Erreichung ihrer unternehmerischen Ziele beratend zu begleiten. Im Leadership-Teil geht es darum, Coaching- und Leadership-Methoden gezielt miteinander zu kombinieren.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Den Abschluss des Studiums bildet die Masterarbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Berufliche Perspektiven</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die&nbsp;praxisbezogene Weiterbildung er&ouml;ffnet Karrierechancen sowohl als Business Coach als auch als zukunftsf&auml;hige F&uuml;hrungskraft.</p>', 'coaching-studium', 'Coaching-Studium (MBA) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Business-Coach werden? Entdecke ein Coaching-Studium für Führungsprofis: ✔ Digital ✔ Flexibel ✔ Praxisfokus. Jetzt entdecken & Leadership Skills boosten!', 10, 'de'),
(17, 'MBA in Mobile & Digital Marketing', 'MBA Mobile & Digital Marketing Degree Program', '<p>Wondering how to become a modern marketer? Here&rsquo;s your answer: with a postgraduate Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing degree. Secure the benefit package for your career: 100% part-time &amp; location-independent. Top MBA studies for decision makers in the field &ndash; practice-focused, innovative &amp; up-to-date. Start any time!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Why Study For An MBA With <em>ONSITES</em>? 7 Reasons</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-focused learning</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality study materials</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Extensive &amp; personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% digital</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>The Digital Marketing Degree At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration<strong> </strong>(MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>: 60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition&nbsp;Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>: Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Become A&nbsp;Digital Marketer From The Comfort Of Your Home</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go digital! Your path to a higher marketing manager salary starts here. The significant growth of the mobile and digital business is driving up the demand for highly skilled professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this Digital Marketing degree you will upgrade your marketing and management knowledge and become well prepared for the latest challenges in digital corporate communication.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The Target Group?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>The program&nbsp;is aimed at professionals and managers in areas such as marketing, advertising, public relations or corporate communications who want to gain digital skills while working and take the next step in their career.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What&rsquo;s The Program About?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this&nbsp;multimodular online program, you will learn how digital business models work and gain a deep understanding of the important role of marketing in the digital transformation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hands-on learning content on Marketing 4.0, Search engine optimization, Social media and Content marketing, and Digital media planning will enable you to profitably organize, manage, market, and implement digital media offerings in your day-to-day work.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of your studies, you will write a master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Job &amp; Career</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This distance learning&nbsp;program qualifies you to take on senior management positions in companies and organizations facing the challenges of digital transformation, as well as to continue your academic career in the form of a doctorate.</p>', 'digital-marketing-degree', 'Mobile & Digital Marketing Degree | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Enhance your marketing career! With our MBA in Mobile & Digital Marketing. ✔ 100% digital ✔ High-quality materials ✔ Personal support. Start now!', 11, 'en'),
(18, 'MBA in Mobile & Digital Marketing', 'MBA Marketing-Studium (Mobile & Digital Marketing)', '<p>Moderner Marketer werden, aber wie? Mit einem postgradualen Marketing-Studium in Digital Marketing. Das Vorteilspaket f&uuml;r Deine Marketing-Karriere. 100% berufsbegleitend &amp; ortsunabh&auml;ngig.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Weiterbildung mit Zukunftsperspektive &ndash; praxisnah, innovativ &amp; hochaktuell. Jetzt starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r ein&nbsp;Marketing-Studium&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertige Studienmaterialien</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Umfassende &amp; pers&ouml;nliche Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>100% digital</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Der MBA im &Uuml;berblick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">&nbsp;</span></strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelorabschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7.500,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Online Marketing-Studium f&uuml;r Digitalprofis</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Digitalgenial! Dein Weg zu einem h&ouml;heren Marketing-Manager-Gehalt startet hier. Das gro&szlig;e&nbsp;Wachstum des Mobile- und Digital-Business treibt die Nachfrage nach topqualifizierten Fachkr&auml;ften nach oben.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mit diesem&nbsp;Master of Business Administration upgradest Du Dein Marketing- und Management-Wissen und wirst bestens gewappnet f&uuml;r die neuesten Herausforderungen in der digitalen Unternehmenskommunikation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Wer ist f&uuml;r diesen&nbsp;MBA geeignet?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Weiterbildung&nbsp;richtet sich an Fach- und F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte in Bereichen wie Marketing, Werbung, Public Relations oder Unternehmenskommunikation, die berufsbegleitend digitale Kompetenzen erlangen und den n&auml;chsten Karriereschritt gehen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Worum geht es in diesem Marketing-Studium?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In diesem&nbsp;multimodularen Studium lernst Du die Funktionsweise digitaler Gesch&auml;ftsmodelle kennen und erlangst ein tiefes Verst&auml;ndnis f&uuml;r die wichtige Rolle des Marketing in der digitalen Transformation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Praxisnahe Inhalte &uuml;ber Marketing 4.0, Suchmaschinenoptimierung, Social Media Marketing und Content Marketing sowie Digital Media Planning bef&auml;higen Dich dazu, digitale Medienangebote im Berufsalltag gewinnbringend zu organisieren, zu steuern, zu vermarkten und umzusetzen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zum Abschluss des Studiums verfasst Du eine Masterarbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beruf &amp; Karriere</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das weiterbildende Fernstudium qualifiziert zur &Uuml;bernahme von leitenden Management-Positionen in Unternehmen und Organisationen, die sich den Herausforderungen&nbsp;der digitalen Transformation stellen, sowie zur Weiterf&uuml;hrung der akademischen Laufbahn in Form einer Promotion.</p>', 'digital-marketing-studium', 'Digital Marketing-Studium (MBA) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Dein digitales Skill-Upgrade. Ein weiterbildendes Marketing-Studium boostet Deinen Marktwert. ✔ Ohne Präsenz ✔ Neben dem Beruf ✔ Ohne Bachelor. Jetzt klicken!', 11, 'de'),
(19, 'MBA in Digital Product Management', 'MBA Digital Product Management Course', '<p>Want to become a next-generation product manager? Expand your digital expertise. With a Digital Product Management course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top distance learning for innovative product managers: 100% free time management &ndash; 100% remote &ndash; 100% up to date! Get ready for the digital future. Boost your professional profile now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Why Go For An MBA With <em>ONSITES</em>?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Strong focus on practice</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality contents</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; extensive support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized education</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>: 12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>: Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>: Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Fit For The Digital Market Of The Future</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go digital! Whether apps, e-books, online courses or cloud services - digital products are revolutionizing the economy. To position digital products and services competitively in the market, digital expertise is one of the most important and sought-after assets in the New Economy. Become part of the next generation of product managers!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is This Product Management Course&nbsp;Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The MBA program is aimed at people with a completed first degree and relevant professional experience who would like to train online to become a Digital Product Manager alongside their job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Contents &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The multimodular MBA program combines business studies with technology studies. You&#39;ll learn to lead teams of experts in creative digital solutions and manage the lifecycle of digital products. To do this, you&#39;ll get to know the most in-demand technologies and familiarize yourself with innovative business and innovation models.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using high-quality Harvard learning materials, you&#39;ll gain cutting-edge knowledge in user experience design, cloud computing, agile product management, web &amp; mobile development, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of your studies, you will demonstrate your ability to work scientifically in the context of a master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Prospects</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This Product Management course of studies&nbsp;qualifies you to take on responsible positions with decision-making authority, whether as a strategic product manager, technical product manager or product owner for digital products.</p>', 'product-management-course', 'Product Management Course Online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Get ready for the digital future. With our MBA in Digital Product Management program. ✔ 100% online ✔ Practical focus ✔ Recognized education. Apply now!', 12, 'en'),
(20, 'MBA in Digital Product Management', 'MBA Produktmanagement-Studium (Digital Product Management)', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest Produktmanager der n&auml;chsten Generation werden? Dann erweitere Dein digitales Fachwissen. Mit einem MBA Produktmanagement-Studium in Digital Product Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top-Fernstudium f&uuml;r innovative Produktmanager: 100% freie Zeiteinteilung &ndash; 100% digital &ndash; 100% aktuell! Mach Dich bereit f&uuml;r die digitale Zukunft. Jetzt Berufsprofil boosten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Warum ein Produktmanagement-Studium mit <em>ONSITES</em>?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hoher Praxisfokus</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hochwertige Inhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#3498db\">H</span><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">ohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pr&auml;senzfrei</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Der MBA auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>: 12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelorabschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7.500,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Topfit f&uuml;r den digitalen Zukunftsmarkt</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Go digital! Ob Apps, E-Books, Online-Kurse oder Cloud-Dienste &ndash; digitale Produkte revolutionieren die Wirtschaft. Um digitale Produkte und Dienstleistungen wettbewerbsf&auml;hig am Markt zu positionieren, ist digitale Fachkompetenz einer der wichtigsten und begehrtesten Assets in der New Economy. Werde Teil der n&auml;chsten Generation von Produktmanagern!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich das Produktmanagement-Studium?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das MBA-Studium in Digital Product Management richtet sich an Personen mit abgeschlossenem Erststudium und einschl&auml;giger Berufserfahrung, die sich neben ihrem Beruf online zum Digital Product Manager ausbilden lassen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das multimodulare Weiterbildungsstudium&nbsp;vereint ein BWL-Studium mit einem Technologie-Studium. Du lernst, Expertenteams f&uuml;r kreative digitale L&ouml;sungen zu leiten und den Lebenszyklus digitaler Produkte zu verwalten. Dazu setzt Du Dich mit den gefragtesten Technologien auseinander und machst Dich mit innovativen Gesch&auml;fts- und Innovationsmodellen vertraut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anhand hochwertiger Harvard-Lernmaterialien erlangst Du topaktuelle Kenntnisse im User Experience Design, Cloud Computing, agilem Produktmanagement, Web &amp; Mobile Development und vielem mehr.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zum Abschluss des Studiums stellst Du Deine F&auml;higkeit zum wissenschaftlichen Arbeiten im Rahmen einer Masterarbeit unter Beweis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Berufliche Perspektiven im digitalen Produktmanagement</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dieses&nbsp;MBA Produktmanagement-Studium qualifiziert Dich zur &Uuml;bernahme von verantwortungsvollen Positionen mit Entscheidungskompetenz, sei es als strategischer Produktmanager, technischer Produktmanager oder Product Owner f&uuml;r digitale Produkte.</p>', 'produktmanagement-studium', 'Produktmanagement-Studium (MBA) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Höheres Produktmanager-Gehalt gefällig? Starte ein weiterbildendes Produktmanagement-Studium. ✔ Digitales Know-how ✔ Online ✔ Maximal flexibel. Jetzt entdecken!', 12, 'de'),
(21, 'MBA in Health Care Management', 'MBA in Health Care Management', '<p>Want to earn a healthcare manager salary? Meet all the requirements of a modern healthcare manager!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this top-notch MBA degree &ndash; no attendance &amp; full flexibility. Gain management skills &amp; give your career a push forward. Study online now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Why Study For An MBA&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Reasons</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-related curriculum</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality learning</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal top support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Internationally recognized qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>MBA Key Facts</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>: Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Language</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Start</strong></span>: Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>7,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study Health Care Management From Any Place You Want</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Innovative healthcare managers are more in demand than ever before. In particular, demographic change in the sector is creating a high demand for highly qualified specialists and managers. The postgraduate interdisciplinary MBA program is your stepping stone towards a healthy career future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The MBA in Health Care Management&nbsp;Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The MBA in Health Care Management program&nbsp;is the right fit for you if you are a healthcare professional, have completed your undergraduate degree, and want to further your education while working to help shape the future of the healthcare sector as a healthcare manager.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Content &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;MBA teaches both healthcare skills and business management skills. In this way, you expand your management know-how in a targeted manner and are optimally prepared for the increased demands placed on healthcare managers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In application-oriented online modules and with the help of high-quality Harvard case studies, you will acquire practice-relevant knowledge in healthcare economics, process and change management, personnel management and strategic management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The program concludes with a master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top Career Opportunities</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After successfully completing the practice-oriented degree program, you will have the necessary leadership, technical, and methodological knowledge to effectively perform a wide range of management tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;MBA in Health Care Management program qualifies you to take on leadership roles in companies and institutions in the healthcare sector, including health insurance companies, clinics, hospitals, care facilities, pharmaceutical companies and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'health-care-management', 'Health Care Management MBA | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Take your healthcare career to new heights. With ONSITES Graduate School\'s MBA in Health Care Management. ✔ Online ✔ Top content ✔ Accredited. Click now!', 13, 'en'),
(22, 'MBA in Gesundheitsmanagement', 'MBA Gesundheitsmanagement', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest ein Gesundheits-Manager-Gehalt erhalten? Dann erf&uuml;lle alle Anforderungen eines modernen Healthcare Managers!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mit einem MBA-Gesundheitsmanagement-Studium der Spitzenklasse &ndash; pr&auml;senzfrei &amp; praxisorientiert. Bequem Managementkompetenzen erlangen &amp; durchstarten. Jetzt online Gesundheitsmanagement studieren!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Gesundheitsmanagement-Studium&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Gr&uuml;nde</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anwendungsorientierte Lehre</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertiges Lernen</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche Top-Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">International anerkannte Qualifikation</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Gesamt&uuml;berblick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>: Master of Business Administration (MBA)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Sprache</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>: Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hren</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>&euro; 7.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Gesundheitsmanagement studieren 100% online</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Innovative Healthcare Manager sind begehrter als je zuvor. Insbesondere der demografische Wandel im Gesundheitsbereich sorgt f&uuml;r einen hohen Bedarf an topqualifizierten Fach- und F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;ften. Das postgraduale interdisziplin&auml;re MBA-Studium ist Dein Sprungbrett in eine gesunde Karriere-Zukunft.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich der&nbsp;MBA Gesundheitsmanagement?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Im MBA Gesundheitsmanagement bist Du richtig, wenn Du Professional im Gesundheitswesen bist, ein abgeschlossenes Erststudium hast und Dich neben Deinem Beruf weiterqualifizieren m&ouml;chtest, um die Zukunft des Gesundheitssektors als Healthcare Manager mitzugestalten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalt &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Studium vermittelt sowohl gesundheitswissenschaftliche als auch betriebswirtschaftliche Kompetenzen. Auf diese Weise erweiterst Du gezielt Dein Management-Know-how und wirst bestens auf die erh&ouml;hten Anforderungen an Healthcare Manager vorbereitet.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In anwendungsorientierten Online-Modulen und anhand hochwertiger Harvard-Fallstudien erlangst Du praxisrelevante Kenntnisse in Gesundheits&ouml;konomie, Prozess- und Change Management, Personalf&uuml;hrung und strategischem Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Den Abschluss des Gesundheitsmanagement-Studiums bildet die Master-Thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top-Karrierechancen im Gesundheitssektor</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nach erfolgreichem Abschluss des praxisorientierten MBA&nbsp;Gesundheitsmanagement verf&uuml;gst Du &uuml;ber das n&ouml;tige F&uuml;hrungs-, Fach- und Methodenwissen, um die vielf&auml;ltigen Management-Aufgaben effektiv ausf&uuml;hren zu k&ouml;nnen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Gesundheitsmanagement-Studium qualifiziert zur &Uuml;bernahme von F&uuml;hrungsaufgaben in Unternehmen und Institutionen im Gesundheitssektor, darunter Krankenkassen, Kliniken, Krankenh&auml;user, Pflegeeinrichtungen, Pharmaunternehmen und mehr.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'gesundheitsmanagement-studium', 'MBA Gesundheitsmanagement | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Deine Karriere als Healthcare Manager startet hier. Entdecke den MBA Gesundheitsmanagement: ✔ Management-Knowhow ✔ Praxisbezug ✔ Präsenzfrei. Jetzt einsteigen!', 13, 'de');
