(23, 'Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)', 'Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)', '<p>Your career as a modern top manager starts here. With a premium-class postgraduate professional doctorate in business administration. No attendance &ndash; no waiting times &ndash; free time management. Study part-time &amp; get your DBA online now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Reasons For A DBA With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-related learning</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Up-to-date&nbsp;learning content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; organizational support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Facts About The DBA </strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Degree</strong></span>: Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Duration</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 to 36 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Start</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 to 180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>MBA/Master&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/doctorate#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Tuition Fee</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>9,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span>: Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Online Doctorate in Business Administration &amp; Economics</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have a master&#39;s degree in economics and want to continue your education while working? Then our postgraduate professional doctorate in economics is the optimal choice for you</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Belongs To TheTarget Group?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This postgraduate professional doctorate program is aimed at real doers who want to flexibly elevate their management career to the highest level alongside their job.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Content &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the help of subject-related Harvard case studies and learning tasks, you will acquire practice-relevant know-how to master future challenges in modern management with confidence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to various specialization options, you can determine the field of study individually according to your personal interests. In the final dissertation, you will deal with a current problem in business and economics related to your professional practice and demonstrate your ability to conduct independent research.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Job Prospects Does A DBA Degree Open Up?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This professional doctorate leads to the postgraduate degree Doctor of Business Administration or Doctor of Economics respectively and qualifies students to assume higher management positions in companies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'dba', 'DBA In 12 Months | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Your ticket to top management. Start a Doctor of Business Administration (DBA) program. ✔ Alongside your job ✔ 100% online ✔ Recognized degree. Start now!', 28, 'en'),
(24, 'Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)', 'Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)', '<p>Deine Karriere als moderner Top-Manager beginnt hier. Mit einem berufsbegleitenden DBA-Studium der Premiumklasse. Ohne Pr&auml;senz &ndash; ohne Wartenzeiten &ndash; freie Zeiteinteilung.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jetzt postgradual Wirtschaftswissenschaften studieren &amp; online Doktor-Titel erlangen!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>DBA mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; Genie&szlig;e 7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Praxisnahes Lernen</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Topaktuelle Lerninhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; organisatorische Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Fakten &amp; Daten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Doctor of Business Administration (DBA/Dr. oec.)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 36 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studienform</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>MBA/Master-Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/doktorat#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>&euro; 9.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Online Doktor-Titel machen im postgradualen DBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du hast einen Master-Abschluss in Wirtschaftswissenschaften und willst Dich berufsbegleitend weiterbilden? Dann ist unser postgraduales Berufsdoktorat in Wirtschaftswissenschaften die optimale Wahl f&uuml;r Dich.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Wer geh&ouml;rt zur Zielgruppe?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das weiterbildende Wirtschaftswissenschaften-Studium richtet sich an echte Macher, die flexibel neben dem Beruf ihre Management-Karriere auf das h&ouml;chste Level heben m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anhand von f&auml;cherbezogenen Harvard-Fallstudien und -Lernaufgaben erlangst Du praxisrelevantes Know-how, um k&uuml;nftige Herausforderungen im modernen Management souver&auml;n zu meistern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dank diverser Spezialisierungsoptionen kannst Du die Studienrichtung individuell gem&auml;&szlig; Deinen pers&ouml;nlichen Interessen bestimmen. In der abschlie&szlig;enden Dissertationsschrift behandelst Du ein aktuelles wirtschaftswissenschaftliches Problem mit Bezug zu Deiner Berufspraxis und stellst Deine F&auml;higkeit zur eigenst&auml;ndigen Forschung unter Beweis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Welche Job-Perspektiven er&ouml;ffnet ein DBA-Studium?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das weiterbildende Berufsdoktorat f&uuml;hrt zum postgradualem Abschluss Doctor of Business Administration bzw. Doctor of Economics und qualifiziert zur &Uuml;bernahme h&ouml;herer Management&auml;tigkeiten in Unternehmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'dba', 'DBA In 1 Jahr | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Mit Vollgas ins Top-Management. Unser DBA bringt Dich an die Spitze. Berufsbegleitend BWL-Doktor werden. ✔ Online ✔ Praxisbezogen ✔ Preiswert. Jetzt klicken!', 28, 'de'),
(25, 'Doctor of Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)', 'Doctor in Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)', '<p>Fancy boosting your business lawyer salary? The online doctorate in law makes it possible. Take your career to the next level &ndash; with a postgraduate professional doctorate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Practical &ndash; tailored &ndash; flexible. For business lawyers with high career potential. Apply now &amp; start your business law doctorate online immediately!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Reasons For A Law Doctorate With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Practice-related learning</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality materials</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; organizational support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% remote</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Details At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Degree</strong></span>: Doctor of Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Duration</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 to 36 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>: Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points:</span> </strong>60 to 180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Master&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/doctorate#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Tuition Fee</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>9,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span><span style=\"color:#3498db\">:</span><strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Doing An Online Doctorate In Business Law While Working</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You already have a Master in Laws as well as several years of professional experience? Then the time has come for the next career step. Position yourself as a law doctor with a postgraduate professional doctorate. Doing an online doctorate in Business Law has never been so convenient.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is This Doctor In Laws Program&nbsp;Designed For?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The postgraduate distance learning program Doctor in&nbsp;Laws is perfectly tailored for working business lawyers who want to pursue a doctorate in law online and give their career a boost.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Content &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Designed as a distance learning program, the entire teaching of the Doctor of Laws program takes place online. The high-quality Harvard learning materials, which you work through in a subject-related manner, ensure a close link between theory and practice. This includes case studies, articles, e-books and online courses. This way, you only learn what you really need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Towards the end of the online doctoral program, you will independently write a dissertation in which you research a current business law problem and develop well-founded solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Prospects</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the additional qualification as Doctor in&nbsp;Laws, nothing stands in the way of an optimized business law salary. Apply now and do your doctorate in business law online!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'doctor-in-laws', 'Doctor In Laws (LL.D.) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Boost your income. Become a Doctor in Laws online at ONSITES Graduate School. ✔ Fair fees ✔ Top flexibility ✔ Accredited program. Start now!', 30, 'en'),
(26, 'Doctor of Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)', 'Jura-Doktor Doctor of Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest Dein Wirtschaftsjurist-Gehalt boosten? Der Jura-Doktor macht&rsquo;s m&ouml;glich. Bringe Deine Karriere auf Draht &ndash; mit einem postgradualen Berufsdoktorat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Praxisnah &ndash; passgenau &ndash; flexibel. F&uuml;r Wirtschaftsjuristen mit hohem Karrierepotential. Jetzt bewerben &amp; sofort Doktorat in Jura online starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r einen Jura-Doktor&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahes Lernen</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertige Materialien</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; organisatorische Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% remote</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Weiterbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alles auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Doctor of Laws (LL.D./Dr. iur.)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 36 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studienform</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Master-Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/doktorat#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>&euro; 9.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><a name=\"_Hlk134435277\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung</strong></span></a><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong> von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Doktor-Titel in Jura online machen neben dem Job</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du hast bereits einen Master in Laws sowie mehrj&auml;hrige Berufserfahrung? Dann ist die Zeit f&uuml;r den n&auml;chsten Karriereschritt gekommen. Positioniere Dich als Jura-Doktor mit einem postgradualen Berufsdoktorat. Doktor in Jura werden war noch nie so bequem.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zielgruppe des Berufsdoktorats</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das postgraduale Fernstudium Doctor of Laws/Doctor iuris ist perfekt zugeschnitten auf berufst&auml;tige Wirtschaftsjuristen, die ein Doktorat in Jura online anstreben und ihrer Karriere einen Schub vorw&auml;rts geben m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalt &amp; Struktur</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Als Fernstudium konzipiert, findet die gesamte Lehre im weiterbildenden Jura-Studium Doctor of Laws/Doctor iuris online statt. F&uuml;r eine enge Verzahnung von Theorie und Praxis sorgen die qualitativ hochwertigen Harvard-Lernmaterialien, die Du f&auml;cherbezogen bearbeitest. Hierzu geh&ouml;ren neben Fallstudien auch Artikel, e-Books und Online-Kurse. So lernst Du nur das, was Du wirklich ben&ouml;tigst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gegen Ende des Berufsdoktorats verfasst Du eigenst&auml;ndig eine Dissertationsschrift, in der Du selbst&auml;ndig ein aktuelles wirtschaftsrechtliches Problem erforschst und dazu fundierte L&ouml;sungen entwickelst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Karriereaussichten als Jura-Doktor</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mit der Zusatzqualifikation als Doctor of Laws/Doctor iuris steht einem optimierten Wirtschaftjurist-Gehalt nichts mehr im Wege. Jetzt bewerben und Dokorat in Jura online machen!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'jura-doktor', 'Jura-Doktor in 12 Monaten | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Gehaltserhöhung gefällig? Werde Jura-Doktor. Die Vorzüge unseres Berufsdoktorats: ✔ Präsenzfrei ✔ Top-Betreuung ✔ Internationale Anerkennung. Jetzt überzeugen!', 30, 'de'),
(27, 'Doctor In Public Health (Dr. PH.)', 'Doctor in Public Health (Dr. PH.)', '<p>Move up the health career ladder! With a postgraduate Doctor in Public Health program. Benefit from the many advantages of our professional doctorate: flexibility &ndash; free time management &ndash; remote learning.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For public health professionals who just want more. Start any time!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top 7 Reasons For A Doctorate With <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-oriented curriculum</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-quality study&nbsp;contents</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; organizational support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% digital</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited education</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Doctor In&nbsp;Public Health In Detail</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Degree</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Doctor of Public Health (Dr. PH.)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Duration</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 to 36 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 to 180 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Master&rsquo;s degree <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/doctorate#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Tuition Fee</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>9,500.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Become Doctor&nbsp;In Public Health in 1 Year</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You&#39;ve got your public health master&#39;s degree or equivalent under your belt, and you&#39;ve come a long way professionally, too. Now the time is ripe for the next step on the career ladder: the professional doctorate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Target Group</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The postgraduate doctorate program is specifically designed for full-time professionals in public health jobs who want to further their professional education to boost their careers as top public health managers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study Content &amp; Program Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a postgraduate professional doctorate, the program&nbsp;imparts application-related knowledge for your individual professional public health practice in several modules. Practical relevance is ensured, among other things, by high-quality Harvard case studies with which you deal in a subject-related manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The final part of the postgraduate public health program involves writing a dissertation. There you will independently deal with a professionally relevant public health problem and develop concrete proposals for solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top Career Perspectives</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As a graduate of the Doctor in&nbsp;Public Health program, you will be qualified to take on sophisticated leadership roles in public health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'doctor-in-public-health', 'Doctor In Public Health In 1 Year | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Secure top public health jobs with ONSITES Graduate School\'s online Doctor in Public Health degree. ✔ Flexible ✔ Practical ✔ Accredited. Apply now!', 29, 'en'),
(28, 'Doctor of Public Health (Dr. PH.)', 'Doctor of Public Health (Dr. PH.)', '<p>Ein gesunder Karriereschub nach vorne! Mit dem Doctor of Public Health. Genial postgradual. Profitiere von den vielen Vorz&uuml;gen unseres Berufsdoktorats: Flexibilit&auml;t &ndash; freie Zeiteinteilung &ndash; pr&auml;senzfreies Lernen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F&uuml;r Public-Health-Profis, die einfach mehr wollen. Sofort einsteigen!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Top-Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r ein Doktorat mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anwendungsorientierte Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-Qualit&auml;tsinhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nlicher &amp; organisatorischer Support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% digital</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Akkreditierte Weiterbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Doctor of Public Health im Detail</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Doctor of Public Health (Dr. PH.)</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 36 Monate</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>: Digital</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 180 ECTS</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Master-Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/doktorat#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>: 9.500,00 &euro;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>).</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beruflich aufsteigen mit postgradualem Public-Health-Studium</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du hast Deinen Public-Health-Master oder einen gleichwertigen Abschluss in der Tasche und bist auch beruflich schon weit gekommen. Nun ist die Zeit reif f&uuml;r den n&auml;chsten Schritt auf der Karriereleiter: das Berufsdoktorat.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>F&uuml;r&nbsp;</strong><strong>wen ist der Doctor of Public Health geeignet?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das postgraduale Programm Doctor of Public Health richtet sich speziell an Vollzeit-Berufst&auml;tige in Public-Health-Jobs, die sich fachlich weiterbilden und karrierem&auml;&szlig;ig als Public-Health-Manager voll durchstarten m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalt &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Als postgraduales Berufsdoktorat vermittelt das Doktoratsstudium in mehreren Modulen anwendungsbezogenes Wissen f&uuml;r Deine individuelle berufliche Public-Health-Praxis. Gew&auml;hrleistet wird der Praxisbezug u.a. durch hochwertige Harvard-Fallstudien, mit denen Du Dich f&auml;cherbezogen auseinandersetzt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der letzte Teil des postgradualen Public-Health-Studiums sieht die Erstellung einer Dissertation vor. Dort setzt Du Dich selbst&auml;ndig mit einem berufsrelevanten Problem im Bereich Public Health auseinander und entwickelst dazu konkrete L&ouml;sungsvorschl&auml;ge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top Berufsperspektiven</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Als Absolvent des Doctor of Public Health-Programms bist Du qualifiziert, anspruchsvolle F&uuml;hrungsaufgaben im &ouml;ffentlichen Gesundheitswesen zu &uuml;bernehmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'doctor-of-public-health', 'Doctor of Public Health in 1 Jahr | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Doctor of Public Health ohne Promotion? Kein Problem mit postgradualem Berufsdoktorat. ✔ 100% online ✔ 100% flexibel ✔ 100% akkreditiert. Jetzt mehr erfahren!', 29, 'de'),
(29, 'CAS in Business Administration', 'CAS Business Administration Course', '<p>You want to develop professionally, but you lack the business know-how? No problem. With this CAS you will quickly gain a solid overview.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience a tailor-made knowledge transfer: extra-occupational, practical &amp; up-to-date. Start now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Reasons For Our&nbsp;Business Administration Course</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-focused education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Cutting-edge&nbsp;content</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Excellent support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Location-independent</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited education</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Our Course At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>: 990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>6-month Online Course To Upgrade Your Career</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You have years of professional experience as a specialist in a company. But your business knowledge leaves a lot to be desired. Many interrelations are still unclear, and you can&#39;t keep up with important topics. This will soon be a matter of the past. This business administration&nbsp;course provides you with compact basic knowledge in just a short time. Exactly what you need!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The CAS Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The certificate course is aimed at experienced professionals across all industries who hold an undergraduate degree and want to quickly acquire basic knowledge and competence in business administration.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Is the Course About?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This CAS offers a solid introduction to the basic BA subjects. Using high-quality Harvard case studies, you will acquire sound basic knowledge that will enable you to immediately apply what you have learned in practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Those with leadership ambitions will be well-served in this CAS as well. For you will also gain rudimentary insights into business management by learning about various management methods for different target groups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of the course, you will have mastered the basic terms, concepts and tools of BA&nbsp;and will be able to participate in business-related arguments and discussions at eye level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Continue To EMBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>This Certificate of Advanced Studies can be studied individually or credited towards the <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/emba\">Executive MBA</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'business-administration-course', 'Business Administration Course | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Become a business expert in 6 months. With our CAS Business Administration course. ✔ No attendance ✔ Flexible ✔ Fair fees ✔ Credit for EMBA. Learn more!', 17, 'en'),
(30, 'CAS in Business Administration', 'CAS BWL-Kurs', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest Dich beruflich weiterentwickeln, aber Dir fehlt das betriebswirtschaftliche Know-how? Kein Problem. Mit dem CAS BWL-Kurs erlangst Du z&uuml;gig einen fundierten Gesamt&uuml;berblick.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Erlebe Wissensvermittlung nach Ma&szlig;: berufsbegleitend, praxisnah &amp; topaktuell. Jetzt online starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">7 Gr&uuml;nde f&uuml;r einen BWL-Kurs mit <em>ONSITES</em></span></strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisfokussierte Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Topaktuelle Inhalte</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Ortsungebunden</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Akkreditierte Weiterbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Facts</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/akkreditierung-und-partner\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>6-monatiger Online-Kurs in BWL</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du hast jahrelange Berufserfahrung als Fachkraft in einem Unternehmen. Doch Dein betriebswirtschaftliches Wissen l&auml;sst zu w&uuml;nschen &uuml;brig. Viele Zusammenh&auml;nge sind noch unklar; bei wichtigen Themen kannst Du nicht mitreden. Das ist bald graue Geschichte. Dieser CAS-Online-Kurs vermittelt Dir kompaktes Grundlagenwissen in nur kurzer Zeit. Genau, was Du brauchst!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich der BWL-Kurs?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das CAS Betriebswirtschaft-Studium&nbsp;richtet sich branchenunabh&auml;ngig an berufserfahrene Fachpersonen mit Erstabschluss, die sich schnell Grundlagenwissen und Mitsprachekompetenz in Betriebswirtschaft aneignen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Welche Inhalte umfasst das weiterbildende Betriebswirtschaft-Studium?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Kurs bietet eine solide Einf&uuml;hrung in die betriebswirtschaftlichen Grundf&auml;cher. Anhand hochwertiger Harvard-Fallstudien erarbeitest Du Dir fundiertes Basiswissen, das Dich dazu bef&auml;higt, das Gelernte sofort in der Praxis anzuwenden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Auch wer F&uuml;hrungsambitionen hat, wird in dieser BWL-Weiterbildung bestens bedient. So erh&auml;ltst Du zudem rudiment&auml;re Einblicke in die Unternehmensf&uuml;hrung, indem Du verschiedene Managementmethoden f&uuml;r verschiedene Zielgruppen kennenlernst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Am Ende des Kurses beherrschst Du die grundlegenden Begriffe, Konzepte und Tools der Betriebswirtschaftslehre und kannst auf Augenh&ouml;he an betriebswirtschaftlichen&nbsp;Argumentationen und Diskussionen teilnehmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiter zum EMBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der&nbsp;CAS BWL-Kurs&nbsp;kann einzeln absolviert&nbsp;oder auf den <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/emba\">EMBA</a>&nbsp;angerechnet werden.</p>', 'bwl-kurs', 'BWL-Kurs mit Zertifikat online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Werde BWL-Experte in 6 Monaten! Mit einem topaktuellen CAS BWL-Kurs. ✔ Alle Basics kompakt ✔ Ortsunabhängig ✔ Anrechnung auf EMBA. Jetzt entdecken.', 17, 'de'),
(31, 'CAS in Leadership & Coaching', 'CAS Leadership & Coaching Course', '<p>Are you a talented manager responsible for the sustainable development of your employees? Then a coaching for leaders is exactly what you need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Become a business coach in 6 months. Besides your job. From any place. Top online training for modern managers. Start immediately!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Coaching Course&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES </em>&ndash; 7 Benefits</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-focused education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Innovative&nbsp;learning content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">First-class support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Location-independent</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited programs</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Details &amp; Facts</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: German or Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Coaching For Leaders In 6 Months</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The coaching market is experiencing rapid development worldwide. This also applies to coaching in leadership. Thus,&nbsp;it&nbsp;has already established itself as a popular tool for employee development. Versatile and experienced managers are increasingly taking on the additional role of internal coaches. This&nbsp;CAS makes you fit for Leadership 2.0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Target Group</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The target group for this&nbsp;CAS program includes business practitioners who want to become professional business coaches, or experienced managers and project leaders who want to specifically expand their leadership skills to include consulting and coaching skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Coaching Course&nbsp;Cover?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS online program provides you with the basic tools to accompany and support people in their individual professional development as a business coach. In cutting-edge online modules, you will learn and apply the essential techniques, tools and methods of successful coaching.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A special focus of the CAS leadership and coaching course&nbsp;is on using coaching aspects in a situation-appropriate way when leading and promoting employees. You will practice what you have learned using realistic case studies with situations from professional and management practice. The practice-oriented online training enables you to competently conduct coaching processes in order to effectively and sustainably support the coachees&#39; further development.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of the training program, you will write a 30-page CAS thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Crediting For MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can take the CAS online course individually or get <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">credit</a> toward the corresponding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/coaching-leadership\">MBA </a>program.</p>', 'coaching-course', 'Leadership & Coaching Course Online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Enhance your leadership skills & become personal coach. With our CAS in Leadership & Coaching course. ✔ 6-month ✔ Online ✔ Credit for MBA. Start now!', 18, 'en');
INSERT INTO `program_translations` (`id`, `name`, `single_page_heading`, `small_desc`, `general_desc`, `text`, `slug`, `meta_title`, `meta_description`, `program_id`, `locale`) VALUES
(32, 'CAS in Leadership & Coaching', 'CAS Weiterbildung Coaching & Leadership', '<p>Du bist eine talentierte F&uuml;hrungskraft und verantwortlich f&uuml;r die nachhaltige Weiterentwicklung der Mitarbeiter? Dann ist eine Personalcoach-Ausbildung genau das, was Du brauchst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Werde Personalcoach in 6 Monaten. Neben Deinem Beruf. Ortsunabh&auml;ngig. Top Online-Weiterbildung f&uuml;r moderne F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte. Sofort einsteigen!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbildung Coaching mit <em>ONSITES </em>&ndash; 7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisfokussierte Ausbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Innovative Lerninhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Ortsungebunden</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Akkreditierte Weiterbildung</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Programmdetails kurz &amp; kompakt</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Deutsch oder Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990,00&nbsp;&euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Personalcoach werden in 6 Monaten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Coaching-Markt verzeichnet weltweit eine rasante Entwicklung. Das gilt auch f&uuml;r das Personal-Coaching. So hat sich Coaching bereits als beliebtes Tool der Mitarbeiterentwicklung etabliert. Vielseitige und erfahrene F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte &uuml;bernehmen immer mehr die zus&auml;tzliche Rolle als interne Personalcoaches. Dieses&nbsp;CAS macht Dich fit f&uuml;r F&uuml;hrung 2.0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zielgruppe</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zur Zielgruppe der Weiterbildung Coaching geh&ouml;ren Berufspraktiker, die professionelle Business-Coaches werden wollen;&nbsp;oder erfahrene F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte und Projektleiter, die ihre F&uuml;hrungskompetenz gezielt um Berater- und Coaching-F&auml;higkeiten erweitern m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Inhalte der Weiterbildung Coaching</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In der CAS-Weiterbildung Coaching &amp; Leadership erh&auml;ltst Du das grundlegende R&uuml;stzeug, um als Businesscoach Menschen bei ihrer individuellen beruflichen Weiterentwicklung zu begleiten und zu unterst&uuml;tzen. In topaktuellen Online-Modulen lernst Du die wesentlichen Techniken, Tools und Methoden erfolgreichen Coachings kennen und anzuwenden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ein besonderer Schwerpunkt des CAS-Kurses liegt darauf, Coachingaspekte situationsgerecht bei der F&uuml;hrung und F&ouml;rderung von Mitarbeitern einzusetzen. Ge&uuml;bt wird das Gelernte anhand von realit&auml;tsnahen Fallstudien mit Situationen aus der Berufs- und F&uuml;hrungspraxis. Die praxisorientierte Online-Weiterbildung bef&auml;higt Dich dazu, Coaching-Prozesse kompetent durchzuf&uuml;hren, um die Weiterentwicklung der Coachees effektiv und nachhaltig zu unterst&uuml;tzen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zum Abschluss der&nbsp;Weiterbildung verfasst Du eine 30-seitige CAS-Arbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung auf MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du kannst den CAS-Kurs einzeln belegen oder Dir auf den entsprechenden&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/coaching-studium\">MBA </a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">anrechnen</a> lassen.</p>', 'weiterbildung-coaching', 'Weiterbildung Coaching online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Personalcoach werden? Die CAS Online Weiterbildung Coaching ist die schnelle Lösung. ✔ 1 Semester ✔ Freie Zeiteinteilung ✔ Anrechnen auf MBA. Jetzt informieren!', 18, 'de'),
(33, 'CAS in Mobile & Digital Marketing', 'CAS Mobile & Digital Marketing Course', '<p>Looking for a cutting-edge further training in marketing? Then this CAS online course is just what you need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Explore the world of digital marketing &ndash; from social media to email &amp; content marketing. Flexible in terms of location and time. Adapt your studies to your professional life. Start any time!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Certificate&nbsp;Course With <em>ONSITES </em>&ndash; 7 Benefits</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High practical relevance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>High-quality&nbsp;learning materials</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Great flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Excellent support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Location-independent</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited distance learning</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Facts</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Qualification</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>: Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Take A Digital Marketing Course Online</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the digital age, the marketing and communications industry is changing at breakneck speed. If you want to survive and thrive in this fast-paced environment, you have to adapt to the changing circumstances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this practice-oriented online training course, you will gain a fundamental understanding of digital trends, technologies, tools and opportunities in modern marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The CAS Online Course Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The continuing education online course is aimed at professional practitioners working in marketing jobs or related fields such as advertising, media, and communications who want to acquire digital marketing know-how or deepen their existing knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Program Overview</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this digital marketing&nbsp;course, you will receive a compact introduction to the world of digital marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After a general overview of the basic operating principles that underlie the digital sector, you&#39;ll learn about key tools such as email and content marketing and their importance in the traditional marketing mix.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Using authentic practical examples and case studies, the course enables you to strategically design and implement digital marketing activities such as online campaigns, but also to measure and optimize them.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The learning content is consolidated within the framework of a final CAS thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Crediting For An MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing course can be taken individually or <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">credited</a>&nbsp;towards the corresponding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/digital-marketing-degree\">MBA </a>&nbsp;program.</p>', 'digital-marketing-course', 'Mobile & Digital Marketing Course | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Level up your marketing skills. With a CAS Digital Marketing Course. ✔ Flexible location & time ✔ Accredited learning ✔ 3 languages. Start any time!', 19, 'en'),
(34, 'CAS in Mobile & Digital Marketing', 'CAS Weiterbildung Marketing (Mobile & Digital Marketing)', '<p>Auf der Suche nach einer topaktuellen Marketing-Weiterbildung? Dann ist dieses CAS in Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing genau das Richtige.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Tauche ein in die Welt des digitalen Marketings &ndash; von Social-Media- bis E-Mail- &amp; Content-Marketing. &Ouml;rtlich &amp; zeitlich flexibel. Passe Dein Studium Deinem Berufsleben an. Jederzeit starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbildung Marketing mit <em>ONSITES </em>&ndash; 7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hoher Praxisbezug</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hochwertige Lernmaterialien</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Gro&szlig;e Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Faire Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Exzellente Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Ortsunabh&auml;ngig</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Akkreditiertes Fernstudium</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Eckdaten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Mobile Marketing &amp; Digital Marketing online studieren</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Im digitalen Zeitalter ver&auml;ndert sich die Marketing- und Kommunikationsbranche mit rasanter Geschwindigkeit. Wer in diesem schnelllebigen Umfeld durchhalten und durchstarten m&ouml;chte, muss sich den ver&auml;nderten Gegebenheiten anpassen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In dieser praxisnahen Online-Weiterbildung erlangst Du ein grundlegendes Verst&auml;ndnis f&uuml;r die digitalen Trends, Technologien, Instrumente und M&ouml;glichkeiten im modernen Marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich die Weiterbildung Marketing?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Weiterbildung richtet sich an Berufspraktiker in Marketing-Jobs oder verwandten Bereichen wie Werbung, Medien und Kommunikation, die sich digitales Know-how aneignen oder bereits vorhandene Kenntnisse vertiefen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Programm&uuml;berblick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In diesem&nbsp;Zertifikatslehrgang erh&auml;ltst Du einen kompakten Einstieg in die Welt des digitalen Marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nach einem allgemeinen &Uuml;berblick &uuml;ber die grundlegenden Funktionsprinzipien, denen die Digitalbranche unterliegt, lernst Du zentrale Instrumente wie E-Mail- und Content-Marketing sowie deren Bedeutung im herk&ouml;mmlichen Marketingmix kennen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Kurs bef&auml;higt Dich anhand von authentischen Praxisbeispielen und Fallstudien dazu, digitale Marketingt&auml;tigkeiten wie Online-Kampagnen strategisch zu entwerfen, umzusetzen, aber auch zu messen und zu optimieren.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gefestigt werden die Lerninhalte im Rahmen einer abschlie&szlig;enden CAS-Arbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung auf MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Weiterbildung Marketing&nbsp;kann einzeln belegt oder auf den entsprechenden&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/digital-marketing-studium\">MBA </a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">angerechnet </a>werden.</p>', 'weiterbildung-marketing', 'Weiterbildung Marketing (CAS) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Schnelleinstieg in Digitales Marketing. Online CAS Weiterbildung Marketing für moderne Marketer. ✔ 1 Semester ✔ 3 Sprachen ✔ Anrechnen auf MBA. Jetzt klicken!', 19, 'de'),
(35, 'CAS in Social Media Management', 'CAS Social Media Management Course', '<p>Career opportunity as a manager for social media &ndash; this is how you seize it. With a part-time social media manager training: 100% digital - free time management - intensive practical knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For newcomers. No previous knowledge required. <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/student-portal\">Apply</a> now &amp; start immediately!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Social Media Management Course With <em>ONSITES - </em>7 Perks</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-based learning</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality study materials</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key&nbsp;Facts About The Online Course</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Qualification</span></strong>: Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Language</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>: 30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span>: Possible<strong> </strong>(<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Social </strong><strong>M</strong><strong>edia </strong><strong>M</strong><strong>anager </strong><strong>T</strong><strong>raining </strong><strong>I</strong><strong>n 6 </strong><strong>M</strong><strong>onths</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>A social media presence has become indispensable for companies, institutions and public bodies in the course of the digital transformation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you want to build a close relationship with your target audience and get to know their needs and preferences, you can no longer avoid an effective social media appearance. Excellent career prospects!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The Course Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS Social Media Management course&nbsp;is aimed at full-time professionals in areas such as marketing, product management, advertising or corporate communications who would like to train as a social media manager while working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Course Content &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As part of various online modules, you will receive a systematic introduction to the central topics of social media and social media management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this program, you will learn everything you need to know to successfully use and manage all common platforms - from the development of an effective social media strategy to the planning, implementation and monitoring of appropriate measures and campaigns to a legally compliant online presence.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examination requirements include the completion of subject-related Harvard case studies and a 30-page CAS thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Continue To Master</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Social Media Management course can be taken either individually or as part of the <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/master-degree/digitalization\">Master in Digitalization</a> and <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/digital-marketing-degree\">MBA in Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing</a> program, respectively.</p>', 'social-media-management-course', 'Social Media Management Course | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Social media manager in 6 months. Take a CAS Social Media Management course. ✔ Online ✔ No prior knowledge required ✔ Credit toward Master\'s/MBA. Apply now!', 20, 'en'),
(36, 'CAS in Social Media Management', 'CAS Weiterbildung Social Media Management', '<p>Karrierechance Soziale Medien &ndash; so ergreifst Du sie. Mit einer zertifizierten Weiterbildung Social Media Management: 100% digital &ndash; freie Zeiteinteilung &ndash; intensives Praxiswissen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F&uuml;r Neueinsteiger. Keine Vorkenntnisse erforderlich. Jetzt <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/bewerbung-studium\">bewerben</a>&nbsp;&amp; sofort starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbildung Social Media Management mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahes Lernen</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hochwertige Studienmaterialien</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Qualifikation</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Facts zum Online-Kurs</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>: Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Sprache</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbildung Social-Media-Management&nbsp;&uuml;ber&nbsp;6 Monate</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eine Pr&auml;senz in den Sozialen Medien ist im Zuge der digitalen Transformation f&uuml;r Unternehmen, Institutionen und &ouml;ffentliche Einrichtungen unverzichtbar geworden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wer eine enge Beziehung zu seiner Zielgruppe aufbauen sowie deren Bed&uuml;rfnisse und Pr&auml;ferenzen kennenlernen m&ouml;chte, kommt an einem wirkungsvollen Auftritt in den sozialen Medien nicht mehr vorbei. Hervorragende Karriere-Aussichten!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich die Fortbildung?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das weiterbildende Social-Media-Management-Studium richtet sich an Vollzeit-Berufst&auml;tige in Bereichen wie Marketing, Produktmanagement, Werbung oder Unternehmenskommunikation, die sich berufsbegleitend zum Manager f&uuml;r Soziale Medien&nbsp;ausbilden lassen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Kursinhalte &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Im Rahmen verschiedener Online-Module erh&auml;ltst Du eine systematische Einf&uuml;hrung in die zentralen Themenbereiche von Social Media und Social Media Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In diesem Lehrgang&nbsp;lernst Du alles, was Du wissen musst, um als Manager f&uuml;r Soziale Medien&nbsp;s&auml;mtliche g&auml;ngige Plattformen erfolgreich zu nutzen und verwalten &ndash; von der Entwicklung einer effektiven Strategie &uuml;ber die Planung, Umsetzung und &Uuml;berwachung von entsprechenden Ma&szlig;nahmen und Kampagnen bis zu einem rechtssicheren Online-Auftritt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zu den Pr&uuml;fungsleistungen z&auml;hlen f&auml;cherbezogene Harvard-Case-Studys sowie eine 30-seitige CAS-Thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiter zum Master</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Weiterbildung&nbsp;Social Media Management kann entweder individuell oder als Teil des&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/master/digitalisierung-studium\">Master Digitalisierung</a> bzw. <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/digital-marketing-studium\">MBA in Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing</a> absolviert werden.</p>', 'weiterbildung-social-media-management', 'Weiterbildung Social Media Management | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Social-Media-Manager in 6 Monaten. Top Weiterbildung Social Media Management. ✔ Präsenzfrei ✔ Ohne Vorkenntnisse ✔ Anrechnung auf Master/MBA. Jetzt bewerben!', 20, 'de'),
(37, 'CAS in SEO Marketing', 'CAS SEO Course For Marketing', '<p>Improve your Google ranking. With up-to-date know-how in search engine optimization marketing. Become a SEO expert in just 6 months &ndash; independent of location &amp; part-time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top continuing education for marketing masters. Because knowledge pays off. Apply now &amp; start anytime!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Benefits Of Our SEO Course</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-based teaching</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top learning content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Details At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span>: </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or similar <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>SEO Course Online For Master Marketers</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Professional online marketing is mandatory for companies in the digital age. If you want to secure a top Google ranking, you have to continuously optimize your performance. A decisive factor in this is effective SEO marketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Only with the right expertise can you reach the top positions. Top career opportunities for SEO&nbsp;specialists!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is This Course Designed For?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;CAS SEO&nbsp;course is aimed at professionals and managers in marketing, product management or advertising who wish to continue their education without interrupting their professional practice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Course Contents</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This&nbsp;certificate online course provides you with practical know-how of search engine optimization within the framework of various modules in order to improve organic rankings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In addition, you will learn the most important aspects of search engine advertising, namely planning, placement and evaluation. You will also gain up-to-date knowledge of digital search engine marketing tools and algorithms.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Examination requirements include working on high-quality Harvard case studies and writing a 30-page CAS thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Building Up To The MBA/Master&#39;s Degree</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS course is offered both separately and as part of an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/digital-marketing-degree\">MBA </a>&nbsp;and <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/master-degree/digitalization\">Master</a>&nbsp;program, respectively.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'seo-course-marketing', 'SEO Course Online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Become a SEO expert in 6 months. With our CAS SEO course. Discover the latest SEO marketing techniques ✔ Part-time ✔ 100% online ✔ Practice-based. Apply now.', 21, 'en'),
(38, 'CAS in SEO Marketing', 'CAS SEO-Kurs für Marketing', '<p>Google-Ranking verbessern, aber wie? Mit aktuellem Know-how in Suchmaschinenmarketing. Werde SEO-Experte in nur 6 Monaten &ndash; ortsunabh&auml;ngig &amp; berufsbegleitend.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top-Weiterbildung f&uuml;r Macher im Marketing. Weil Wissen sich auszahlt. Jetzt anmelden &amp; jederzeit starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>7 Vorteile unseres SEO-Kurses</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top Lerninhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Qualifikation</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Details auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>: 6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span>: </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span>: </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span>: </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>SEO-Kurs f&uuml;r&nbsp;Marketing-Magier</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ein professionelles Online-Marketing ist f&uuml;r Unternehmen im digitalen Zeitalter obligatorisch. Wer sich ein Top-Google-Ranking sichern will, muss seine Performance kontinuierlich optimieren. Ein entscheidender Faktor dabei ist ein effektives Suchmaschinenmarketing.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nur mit dem richtigen Fachwissen gelangt man auf die obersten Positionen. Top-Karrierechancen f&uuml;r SEO-Spezialisten!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zielgruppe des Online-Kurses</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der SEO-Kurs richtet sich an Fach- und F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte im Marketing, Produktmanagement oder in der Werbung, die sich fortbilden m&ouml;chten, ohne die berufliche Praxis zu unterbrechen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Kursinhalte</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dieser&nbsp;Online-Kurs mit Zertifikat vermittelt Dir im Rahmen verschiedener Module praxisbezogenes Know-how der Suchmaschinenoptimierung, um organische Rankings zu verbessern.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Daneben lernst Du die wichtigsten Aspekte der Suchmaschinenwerbung kennen, n&auml;mlich Planung, Schaltung und Auswertung. Au&szlig;erdem erh&auml;ltst Du topaktuelle Kenntnisse zu digitalen Suchmaschinenmarketing-Tools und Algorithmen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Als Pr&uuml;fungsleistungen bearbeitest Du hochwertige Harvard-Fallstudien und verfasst eine 30-seitige CAS-Arbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Aufbauen zum Master/MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS SEO-Kurs&nbsp;wird sowohl separat als auch als Teil des Master-Studiums <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/digital-marketing-studium\">MBA in Mobile and Digital Marketing</a> bzw. <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/master/digitalisierung-studium\">Master Digitalisierung</a>&nbsp;angeboten.</p>', 'seo-kurs', 'SEO-Kurs Marketing | ONSITES Graduate School', 'SEO-Experte in 6 Monaten. Online SEO-Kurs für Marketing-Magier ✔ Freie Zeiteinteilung ✔ Soforteinstieg ✔ Auf Master/MBA anrechnen. Jetzt informieren!', 21, 'de'),
(39, 'CAS in Creative Marketing & Copywriting', 'CAS Creative Marketing & Copywriting Course', '<p>Wondering how to become a copywriter and get a top-paying copywriting job? The answer is simple: With the right copywriting course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Become a creative copywriter in just 6 months &ndash; part-time &amp; from the comfort of your home. Secure your place now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Why Take A Copywriting Course With <em>ONSITES</em>? 7 Reasons</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>High practical focus</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">First-class learning materials</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited certificate</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Data</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Study</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Learn How To Become A&nbsp;Copywriter in 6 Months</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Copywriting jobs are among the most sought-after and promising jobs in marketing. The need for creative minds who can write promotional copy with originality and persuasiveness is high and growing rapidly. More and more companies are realizing the value of sales-boosting online content.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>But to stand out from the crowd of copywriters, you need a knowledge edge. In this course, you&#39;ll get the know-how of experienced industry professionals - perfectly packaged in high-quality Harvard learning content!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is This Course Designed For?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This CAS program is designed for full-time marketing and content writing professionals who have an undergraduate degree and want to train as a copywriter while working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Copywriting&nbsp;Course Cover?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS&nbsp;program gives you access to the coveted field of advertising by teaching you creative writing skills and conceptual thinking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through a variety of hands-on modules, you&#39;ll learn to create strategic copy that&#39;s a perfect fit for different media and social channels. Whether it&#39;s slogans, headlines, advertising campaigns or corporate websites: You&#39;ll develop your own ideas and concepts for engaging advertising content and familiarize yourself with the different styles and techniques of copywriting.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of the program, you will write a 30-page CAS thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Advancing To The MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS course can be taken individually or as part of the <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/digital-marketing-degree\">MBA in Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'copywriting-course', 'Copywriting Course Online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Become a creative copywriter in just 6 months. With a Creative Marketing & Copywriting course! ✔ Part-time ✔ Digital ✔ Practical focus. Apply today!', 22, 'en'),
(40, 'CAS in Creative Marketing & Copywriting', 'CAS Creative Marketing & Copywriting-Kurs', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest in einem topbezahlten Copywriter-Job arbeiten? Kein Problem mit dem&nbsp;richtigen Copywriting-Kurs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Kreativer Copywriter werden in nur 6 Monaten &ndash; berufsbegleitend &amp; bequem von zu Hause. Jetzt Studienplatz sichern &amp; sofort Copywriting lernen!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Copywriting-Kurs&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; aus 7 Gr&uuml;nden</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hoher Praxisfokus</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Lernmaterialien</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Keine Pr&auml;senzzeiten</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkanntes Zertifikat</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Unser Copywriting-Kurs auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>: Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Copywriting lernen mit Harvard-Prestige</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Copywriter-Jobs z&auml;hlen zu den gefragtesten und zukunftstr&auml;chtigsten T&auml;tigkeiten im Marketing. Der Bedarf an kreativen K&ouml;pfen, die mit Originalit&auml;t und &Uuml;berzeugungskraft werbewirksame Texte schreiben k&ouml;nnen, ist hoch und steigt rasant. Immer mehr Firmen realisieren den Wert von verkaufsstarken Online-Inhalten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Aber um sich von der breiten Masse an Copywriters abzuheben, brauchst Du einen Wissensvorsprung. In diesem Copywriter-Kurs erh&auml;ltst Du das Know-how erfahrener Branchenprofis &ndash; perfekt geb&uuml;ndelt in hochwertigen Harvard-Lerninhalten!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich der Kurs?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Copywriting-Kurs richtet sich an Vollzeit-Berufst&auml;tige im Bereich Marketing und Content Writing, die einen ersten Hochschulabschluss haben und sich neben dem Beruf zum Copywriter ausbilden lassen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Was beinhaltet der Copywriting-Kurs?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Kurs verschafft Dir den Zugang zum begehrten Bereich der Werbung, indem er Dir kreative Schreibf&auml;higkeiten und konzeptuelles Denken vermittelt.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In verschiedenen praxisbezogenen Modulen lernst Du, strategische Texte passgenau f&uuml;r unterschiedliche Medien und soziale Kan&auml;le zu erstellen. Ob Slogan, &Uuml;berschriften, Werbekampagnen oder Unternehmenswebsites: Du entwickelst eigene Ideen und Konzepte f&uuml;r ansprechende Werbeinhalte und machst Dich mit den verschiedenen Stilen und Techniken des Werbetextens vertraut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zum Abschluss des Kurses verfasst Du eine 30-seitige CAS-Arbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Aufbauen zum MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Copywriting-Kurs kann einzeln oder als Teil des <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/digital-marketing-studium\">MBA in Mobile &amp; Digital Marketing </a>belegt werden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'copywriting-kurs', 'Copywriting-Kurs mit Zertifikat | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Copywriter werden in nur 6 Monaten. Mit aktuellem CAS Copywriting-Kurs. ✔ Digital ✔ Flexibel ✔ Soforteinstieg ✔ Anrechnung auf MBA. Jetzt mehr erfahren!', 22, 'de');
