(41, 'CAS in Digital Product Management', 'CAS Digital Product Management Certificate', '<p>Want to increase your product manager salary? Get a Digital Product Management certificate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top advanced training&nbsp;for decision-makers in product management: part-time &ndash; job-related &ndash; up-to-date! <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/student-portal\">Apply</a> now to use the digital skills shortage for your benefit!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Product Management&nbsp;Certificate&nbsp;With <em>ONSITES </em>&ndash;&nbsp;7 Benefits</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-based learning</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High-quality study content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized certificate</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Facts At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Start</strong></span>: Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong>&nbsp;</strong>990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>: Possible<strong> </strong>(<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Boost Your Salary With A Product Management Certificate</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Career acceleration with digital transformation! In the age of digitalization, the need for highly qualified product managers and product owners is enormous. Nevertheless, there is a lack of sufficient expertise for the management of specifically digital products. Seize this unique opportunity!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Which Target Group Is The CAS Online Course Designed For?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The certificate course&nbsp;is designed for full-time decision-makers in the field who want to continue their education while working and increase their salary. In addition, the CAS is also suitable as continuing education for professions on the periphery, including product marketing managers or data analysts.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study Contents &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Through several online modules, you&#39;ll learn all the essential concepts, methods, and technologies to effectively plan, develop, manage, and implement digital products and services.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The learning content includes high-quality Harvard case studies, articles, and online courses that you work on in a subject-specific manner.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>At the end of the six-month&nbsp;program, you will complete a written, 30-page CAS thesis on a current problem in the field of digital product management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study For A MBA&nbsp;Degree</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can complete the product management course&nbsp;either individually or as part of the corresponding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/product-management-course\">MBA </a>&nbsp;program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'digital-product-management-certificate', 'Digital Product Management Certificate | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Digital product manager in 1 semester. With a Digital Product Management certificate course. ✔ No attendance ✔ No waiting times ✔ Highly flexible. Apply today!', 23, 'en'),
(42, 'CAS in Digital Product Management', 'CAS Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung', '<p>Produktmanager-Gehalt steigern leicht gemacht. Profitiere vom digitalen Fachkr&auml;ftemangel. Mit einem CAS-Online-Studium in Digital Product Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Top-Weiterbildung f&uuml;r Entscheider im Produktmanagement: berufsbegleitend studieren &ndash; berufsbezogen lernen &ndash; beruflich durchstarten! Jetzt <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/bewerbung-studium\">anmelden</a>!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung mit <em>ONSITES - </em>7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Praxisnahes Lernen</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Hochwertige Studieninhalte</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">100% online</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkanntes Zertifikat</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Fakten auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studienform</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich<strong> </strong>(<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Produktmanager-Gehalt boosten mit CAS-Studium</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Karrierechance digitale Transformation! Im Zeitalter der Digitalisierung ist der Bedarf an hochqualifizierten Produktmanagern und Produktverantwortlichen enorm. Gleichwohl besteht ein Mangel an ausreichender Fachkompetenz f&uuml;r das Management von spezifisch digitalen Produkten. Ergreife diese einmalige Gelegenheit!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>F&uuml;r welche Zielgruppe ist der Online-Kurs konzipiert?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung&nbsp;richtet sich an Vollzeit-Entscheider in diesem Bereich, die sich berufsbegleitend weiterbilden und ihr Gehalt steigern m&ouml;chten. Daneben eignet sich der Lehrgang&nbsp;auch als Fortbildung f&uuml;r Berufe in der Peripherie, darunter Produkt-Marketing-Manager oder Datenanalysten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studieninhalte &amp; Aufbau </strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In mehreren Online-Modulen lernst Du alle wesentlichen Konzepte, Methoden und Technologien kennen, um digitale Produkte und Dienstleistungen effektiv zu planen, entwickeln, steuern und umzusetzen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zu den Lerninhalten geh&ouml;ren hochwertige Harvard-Fallstudien, -Artikel und -Onlinekurse, die Du f&auml;cherbezogen bearbeitest. Am Ende des sechsmonatigen CAS-Studiums verfasst Du eine schriftliche, 30-seitige CAS-Arbeit zu einem aktuellen Problem im Bereich des digitalen Produktmanagement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>CAS auf MBA-Studium anrechnen lassen</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Du kannst die Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung&nbsp;entweder einzeln oder als Teil des entsprechenden&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/produktmanagement-studium\">MBA-Studiums </a>&nbsp;absolvieren.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'produktmanagement-weiterbildung', 'Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung (CAS) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Digitaler Produktmanager in 1 Semester. Mit zertifizierter Produktmanagement-Weiterbildung. ✔ Keine Präsenz ✔ Keine Wartezeiten ✔ Topflexibel. Jetzt überzeugen!', 23, 'de'),
(43, 'CAS in Cyber Security', 'CAS Cyber Security Course', '<p>Do you want to make a career in preventing cybercrime? Then our online cyber security course is the right choice for you. Become an IT security expert in just 6 months &ndash; part-time, practice-oriented &amp; without deep technical knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Entry possible at any time. Apply now &amp; secure career benefits!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Cyber Security Course With <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Benefits</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-related education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">First-class study content</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Key Facts At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>: Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span>: </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>: 30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or similar <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Partake In A&nbsp;Cyber&nbsp;Security Course Without Major Prior Knowledge</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the digital era, no company can ignore the issue of IT security. If you want to protect yourself sustainably against devastating hacker attacks and security breaches, you have to have expert knowledge. That&#39;s why experts are more in demand than ever. The CAS program&nbsp;gives you the expertise you need!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The Course Aimed At?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The online&nbsp;course is aimed at professionals and executives in the fields of risk management and project management who want to acquire valuable IT security know-how on a part-time basis in order to take the next step in their careers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Program&nbsp;Cover?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Secure for sure. The program&nbsp;provides you with a comprehensive understanding of the field, from the technical basics to operating systems, networks, data transmission and cyber security management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In several modules you will learn to identify security gaps and vulnerabilities in the system and to take preventive measures. You will be enabled to conduct and evaluate risk analyses and to derive effective protection guidelines and measures on this basis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the last part of the six-month course, you will independently write a CAS thesis in which you deal with a current problem in the field and develop practical solutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Continue to MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The course can be taken separately or as part of the corresponding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/cyber-security-degree\">MBA </a>&nbsp;program.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'cyber-security-course', 'Cyber Security Course Online | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Ready to launch your cyber security career? Our online IT Security course has got you covered. ✔ High flexibility ✔ Accredited ✔ No attendance. Learn more!', 24, 'en'),
(44, 'CAS in Cyber Security', 'CAS IT Sicherheit-Studium', '<p>Du willst mit Sicherheit Karriere machen? Dann ist unser IT-Sicherheit-Studium die richtige Wahl. Werde IT-Sicherheitsexperte in nur 6 Monaten &ndash; berufsbegleitend, praxisnah &amp; ohne tiefe technische Vorkenntnisse.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Einstieg jederzeit m&ouml;glich. Jetzt bewerben &amp; Karrierevorteile nutzen!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>IT-Sicherheit-Studium&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Studieninhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Ohne Pr&auml;senz</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannte Qualifikation</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alles auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studienform</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>IT Security studieren&nbsp;ohne gro&szlig;e Vorkenntnisse</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>An dem Thema IT-Sicherheit kommt in der Digital&auml;ra kein Unternehmen mehr vorbei. Wer sich nachhaltig vor verheerenden Hackerangriffen und Sicherheitsl&uuml;cken sch&uuml;tzen m&ouml;chte, muss sich bestens auskennen. Darum sind Cyber-Security-Experten gefragter denn je. Im weiterbildenden CAS IT-Sicherheit-Studium&nbsp;erh&auml;ltst Du die Expertise, die Du brauchst &ndash; ganz sicher!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich der Kurs?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Online-Kurs mit Zertifikat richtet sich an Fach- und F&uuml;hrungskr&auml;fte in den Bereichen Risikomanagement und Projektmanagement, die sich nebenberuflich wertvolles Know-how in IT-Security aneignen m&ouml;chten, um den n&auml;chsten Karriereschritt zu gehen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Was beinhaltet das Programm?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Online-Kurs vermittelt Dir ein umfassendes Verst&auml;ndnis von IT-Sicherheit, angefangen von den technischen Grundlagen &uuml;ber Betriebssysteme, Netzwerke und Daten&uuml;bertragung bis zum Cyber-Security-Management.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In mehreren Modulen lernst Du, Sicherheitsl&uuml;cken und Schwachstellen im System zu identifizieren und pr&auml;ventive Ma&szlig;nahmen zu ergreifen. Du wirst dazu bef&auml;higt, Risikoanalysen vorzunehmen, auszuwerten und auf dieser Basis effektive Schutzrichtlinien und -ma&szlig;nahmen abzuleiten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Im letzten Teil des sechsmonatigen Kurses verfasst Du eigenst&auml;ndig eine CAS-Thesis, in der Du Dich mit einem aktuellen Problem im Bereich IT-Sicherheit befasst und L&ouml;sungsans&auml;tze f&uuml;r die Praxis entwickelst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiter zum MBA</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der Online-Kurs kann separat studiert oder oder auf das entsprechende&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/cyber-security-studium\">MBA </a>-Studium&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">angerechnet</a> werden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'it-sicherheit-studium', 'IT-Sicherheit-Studium (CAS online) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Cyber-Security-Experte in 6 Monaten. Online IT-Sicherheit-Studium mit Zertifikat. ✔ Flexibel ✔ Praxisnah ✔ Ohne große Vorkenntnisse. Jetzt klicken!', 24, 'de'),
(45, 'CAS in Health Care Management', 'CAS Health Care Management Course', '<p>Do you want to lead health care teams and make major decisions, but lack the leadership skills? This part-time certificate course online is just what you need.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In this CAS you get the tools to become a modern leader. Experience a knowledge transfer at eye level: application-oriented, up-to-date &amp; 100% remote. <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/student-portal\">Apply</a>&nbsp;now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Health Care Management&nbsp;Course With <em>ONSITES</em></strong> <strong>&ndash; 7 Reasons</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">High practical relevance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">First-class learning contents</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Low fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Accredited qualification</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>All Facts &amp; Data At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Qualification</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Duration</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>6 months</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Form of Study</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Language</strong></span>: English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Start</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>: 30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Admission Requirements</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/cas-online#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Tuition Fee</strong></span>:&nbsp;990.00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Transfer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Become A Health Care Manager In Just 6 Months</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Leadership in health care facilities is complex. From employee development to process control and consideration of economic and legal aspects - a modern health care manager has an enormous amount to do. The prerequisite for this is sound specialist knowledge and specific skills.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this&nbsp;CAS you will receive the necessary basic equipment. Go for it!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Who Is The CAS Course Designed For?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The CAS in Health Care Management Course&nbsp;is aimed at individuals with an undergraduate degree and/or professional experience in the health care sector who wish to assume leadership responsibilities in health care institutions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The target group also includes professionals who already have basic leadership experience and are looking to deepen their leadership skills with an additional qualification.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>What Does The Course Cover?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The certificate course CAS in Health Care Management provides fundamental expertise for successful employee leadership and the goal-oriented management of teams within health care organizations.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>After a general overview of the current framework conditions in the healthcare sector, you will learn how successful leadership can be achieved under these conditions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To this end, you will be familiarized with common business administration processes and instruments that will enable you to apply management methods in an economically sensible and benefit-oriented manner in everyday management tasks.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>What is learned is consolidated in high-quality Harvard case studies with strong practical relevance as well as a 30-page CAS thesis at the end of the course.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Course Towards MBA Degree</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This course can be taken separately or <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">credited</a> toward the corresponding&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba/health-care-management\">MBA</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'health-care-management-course', 'Health Care Management Course | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Become a modern health care manager in just 6 months. With a CAS Health Care Management course. ✔ Specialized knowledge ✔ Part-time ✔ Accredited. Apply now!', 25, 'en'),
(46, 'CAS in Health Care Management', 'CAS in Management im Gesundheitswesen', '<p>Du m&ouml;chtest Gesundheitsteams leiten und wichtige Entscheidungen treffen, aber Dir fehlt die F&uuml;hrungskompetenz? Dann ist diese berufsbegleitende Weiterbildung genau das, was Du brauchst.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In diesem CAS erh&auml;ltst Du das R&uuml;stzeug zur modernen F&uuml;hrungskraft. Erlebe Wissenstransfer auf Augenh&ouml;he: anwendungsorientiert, hochaktuell &amp; 100% remote. Jetzt <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/bewerbung-studium\">anmelden</a>!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbilden&nbsp;mit <em>ONSITES</em></strong> <strong>&ndash; 7 Vorteile</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hoher Praxisbezug</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Lerninhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Topflexibel</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top-Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Keine Pr&auml;senz</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Alle Eckdaten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Abschluss</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Certificate of Advanced Studies (CAS)</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Dauer</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>6 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studienform</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Sprache</strong></span>: Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Beginn</strong></span>: Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Credit Points</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>30 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/cas-online#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studiengeb&uuml;hr</strong></span>:&nbsp;990,00 &euro;</li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Anrechnung von Credits</strong></span>:<strong> </strong>M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Weiterbilden&nbsp;in nur 6 Monaten</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>F&uuml;hrung in Gesundheitseinrichtungen ist komplex. Von Mitarbeiterf&ouml;rderung &uuml;ber Prozesssteuerung bis hin zur Ber&uuml;cksichtigung &ouml;konomisch-rechtlicher Aspekte &ndash; eine moderne F&uuml;hrungskraft leistet enorm viel. Voraussetzung daf&uuml;r sind ein fundiertes Fachwissen und spezifische F&auml;higkeiten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mit dem CAS in Management im Gesundheitswesen&nbsp;erh&auml;ltst Du die n&ouml;tige Grundausstattung. F&uuml;r eine F&uuml;hrung, die funktioniert.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>An wen richtet sich die Weiterbildung?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die CAS-Weiterbildung Management im&nbsp;Gesundheitswesen&nbsp;richtet sich an Personen mit Erstabschluss und/oder Berufserfahrung im Gesundheitssektor, die F&uuml;hrungsverantwortung in Gesundheitsinstitutionen &uuml;bernehmen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ebenfalls zur Zielgruppe geh&ouml;ren Fachkr&auml;fte, die bereits &uuml;ber grundlegende F&uuml;hrungserfahrung verf&uuml;gen und ihre F&uuml;hrungskompetenz mit einer Zusatzqualifikation zu vertiefen suchen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Welche Inhalte umfasst der Lehrgang?</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Weiterbildungskurs Management im&nbsp;Gesundheitsmanagement vermittelt grundlegendes Fachwissen f&uuml;r erfolgreiche Mitarbeiterf&uuml;hrung und das zielgerechte Leiten von Teams innerhalb von Gesundheitsorganisationen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nach einem allgemeinen &Uuml;berblick &uuml;ber die gegenw&auml;rtigen Rahmenbedingungen des Gesundheitssektors lernst Du, wie erfolgreiche F&uuml;hrung unter diesen Bedingungen erreicht werden kann.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Zu diesem Zweck wirst Du mit den g&auml;ngigen betriebswirtschaftlichen Prozessen und Instrumenten vertraut gemacht, die Dich dazu bef&auml;higen, Management-Methoden &ouml;konomisch sinnvoll und nutzenorientiert im F&uuml;hrungsalltag einzusetzen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Gefestigt wird das Gelernte in hochwertigen Harvard-Fallstudien mit starkem Praxisbezug sowie einer 30-seitigen CAS-Arbeit am Ende des Kurses.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Kurs anrechnen auf MBA-Studium</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Der CAS-Kurs Management im&nbsp;Gesundheitswesen&nbsp;kann separat absolviert oder auf den entsprechenden&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba/gesundheitsmanagement-studium\">MBA </a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">angerechnet</a> werden.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'management-im-gesundheitswesen', 'Management im Gesundheitswesen (CAS) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Healthcare-Manager in nur 6 Monaten. Mit dem CAS in Management im Gesundheitswesen. ✔ Ortsunabhängig ✔ Praxisorientiert ✔ Anrechenbar auf MBA. Jetzt entdecken!', 25, 'de'),
(49, 'MBA in Cyber Security', 'MBA Cyber Security Degree', '<p>Better safe than sorry! Start your career as a top trained IT manager. Our MBA Cyber Security degree makes it possible.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Experience a part-time distance learning program lie never before: practice-oriented, presence-free &amp; price-effective. Start any time. Apply for your postgraduate degree now!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Cyber Security Degree With <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; Top 7 Reasons</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Practice-oriented education</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Top-quality study content</strong></span></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Top&nbsp;flexibility</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Fair fees</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Personal &amp; extensive support</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">No attendance</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Recognized degree</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Our MBA Degree At A Glance</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Degree</span></strong>: Master of Business Administration</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Duration</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 to 24 months</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Form of Studies</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Language</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>English, German &amp; Russian</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Start</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Anytime</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 to 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Admission Requirements</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or equivalent <a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/mba#requirements\">(Learn more)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Tuition Fee</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>&euro; 7.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Transfer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Possible (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/en/recognition-of-prior-learning\">Learn more</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Secure Your Career Future With A Cyber Security Degree</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Security comes first! The need for well-trained cyber IT security experts is growing rapidly. The reasons: the ongoing shortage of skilled workers in the IT sector and the frightening reality of increasing cyber attacks. Take advantage of this unique career opportunity &ndash; with a distance learning MBA degree in IT Security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Target Group</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The degree is tailored for full-time professionals with a bachelor&#39;s degree or equivalent who want to train as an cyber IT security manager while working.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Study Contents &amp; Structure</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The multi-module program provides you with the key competencies of an IT manager. First, you will gain a basic understanding of how organizations and companies develop information systems and use them for their competitiveness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the main part of this master of business administration program, you will learn the processes and (technical) means to prevent cyber risks in a planned and effective way, thus ensuring a high level of IT security.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The final phase consists of writing a master&#39;s thesis.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Career Prospects</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The MBA program qualifies you for professional jobs as an IT manager in the areas of threat analysis, network security and cyber defense, among others.</p>', 'cyber-security-degree', 'Cyber Security Degree Online (MBA) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Defeat hackers with ONSITES Graduate School\'s MBA in Cyber Security. ✔ At your own pace ✔ 100% online ✔ Accredited qualification. Start anytime!', 14, 'en'),
(50, 'MBA in Cyber Security', 'MBA Cyber Security-Studium', '<p>Mit Sicherheit nach oben! Starte Deine Karriere als topausgebildeter IT-Manager. Unser MBA Cyber-Security-Studium macht&rsquo;s m&ouml;glich.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Erlebe ein berufsbegleitendes Fernstudium der Premiumklasse: praxisorientiert, pr&auml;senzfrei &amp; preiswert. Schnell bewerben und sofort starten!</p>', '-', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Cyber Security studieren mit <em>ONSITES</em> &ndash; 7 Top-Gr&uuml;nde</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Praxisnahe Lehre</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Erstklassige Inhalte</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Hohe Flexibilit&auml;t</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Niedrige Geb&uuml;hren</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Pers&ouml;nliche &amp; umfassende Betreuung</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Keine Pr&auml;senz</span></strong></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anerkannter Abschluss</span></strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"orangeBox\" style=\"background:#eeeeee; border:1px solid #cccccc; padding:5px 10px\">\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Unser Cyber-Security-Studium auf einen Blick</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Abschluss</span></strong>: Master of Business Administration</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Dauer</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>12 bis 24 Monate</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studienform</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Digital</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Sprache</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Englisch, Deutsch &amp; Russisch</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Beginn</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Jederzeit</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Credit Points</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>60 bis 120 ECTS</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Zulassungsvoraussetzungen</span></strong>:<strong> </strong>Bachelor- oder gleichwertiger Abschluss <a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/mba#requirements\">(Mehr erfahren)</a></li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Studiengeb&uuml;hr</span></strong>: &euro; 7.500,00</li>\r\n	<li><strong><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Anrechnung von Credits</span></strong>: M&ouml;glich (<a href=\"https://graduate.me/de/studium-verkuerzen\">Mehr erfahren</a>)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Cyber Security-Master im Fernstudium</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Cyber Security studieren? Aber sicher! Der Bedarf an gut ausgebildeten IT-Sicherheits-Experten steigt rasant. Die Gr&uuml;nde: der anhaltende Fachkr&auml;ftemangel im IT-Sektor und die beunruhigende Realit&auml;t zunehmender Cyberangriffe. Nutze diese einmalige Karrierechance &ndash; mit dem MBA-Fernstudium in IT-Sicherheit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Zielgruppe</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das Programm ist ma&szlig;geschneidert f&uuml;r Vollzeit-Berufst&auml;tige mit Bachelor- oder gleichwertigem Abschluss, die sich neben ihrem Beruf zum Manager f&uuml;r IT-Sicherheit ausbilden lassen m&ouml;chten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Studieninhalte &amp; Aufbau</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das multimodulare Cyber-Security-Studium vermittelt Dir die Schl&uuml;sselkompetenzen eines IT-Managers. Zun&auml;chst erlangst Du ein grundlegendes Verst&auml;ndnis daf&uuml;r, wie Organisationen und Unternehmen Informationssysteme entwickeln und f&uuml;r ihre Wettbewerbsf&auml;higkeit einsetzen.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Im Hauptteil des Cyber-Security-Studiums lernst Du die Prozesse und (technischen) Mittel kennen, um Cyberrisiken planm&auml;&szlig;ig und effektiv vorzubeugen und so ein hohes Ma&szlig; an IT-Sicherheit zu gew&auml;hrleisten.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Die letzte Phase besteht in der Erstellung einer Masterarbeit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><strong>Karrierechancen im Bereich IT Security</strong></span></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Das MBA-Studium qualifiziert Dich u.a. f&uuml;r berufliche T&auml;tigkeiten als IT-Manager in den Bereichen Gef&auml;hrdungsanalyse, Netzwerksicherheit und Cyber-Abwehr.</p>', 'cyber-security-studium', 'Cyber-Security-Studium (MBA) | ONSITES Graduate School', 'Mit Sicherheit Karriere machen. Starte ein MBA Cyber Security-Studium. Studiere ✔ im eigenen Tempo ✔ an jedem Ort ✔ mit persönlichem Mentor. Jetzt klicken!', 14, 'de');
